\id JHN - MPOTO Bible Version 
\h Yohana 
\toc1 Malobhi Manyahi ngati moghalembakike na Yohana 
\toc2 Yohana 
\toc3 Yoha 
\mt2 Malobhi Manyahi ngati moghalembakike na 
\mt1 Yohana 
\imt1 Ulongulelo 
\ip Malobhi Manyahi ngati moghalembakike na Yohana nde chimu cha hitabu ncheche ya Lulaghilu Lwahenu yeilongalela matamu ghaka Yesu Kristo. Kila chimu cha hitabu yeniheyi chilowakeka “Injili,” lilobhi ambalu ndandi jaki nde “Malobhi Manyahi.” Hitabu yenu ikalembakiki baada ja kupotela kwaka Yesu. Na ikalembakiki na Matayo, Mako, Luka na Yohana. Malobhi Manyahi ngati moghalembakike na Yohana ghakalembakiki mu majomukanelu gha chaka cha 90 baada ja kubhelakeka Yesu Kristo. Hata koni chitabu ngachekipwagha kubha Yohana nde joakalembike, ntundu wa kulemba kwaki ulengana namaa na ghola ghoubhile mu baluwa ya 1 Yohana, 2 Yohana, na 3 Yohana. Bhalemba bhakumu bha mwande bhundongalela Yohana kubha akatami ku muchi wa ku Efeso chikahi chenihechi, bhela iwezikana kubha chitabu chenihechi chakalembakiki ku Efeso. 
\ip Yohana alongela hotuhotu kubha ndandi ja kulemba chitabu chenu nde kubhajangatila bhandu bhaweza kuhobhalela kubha Yesu nde Kristo, Mwana waka Chapanga joabhi mwome 20:31. Kwa kuhobhalela bhenibhela tupata womi kwa lihina laki. Injili jaka Yohana kwa ntundu ghonge ngachejilengana na Injili yengi itatu yela. Yohana akabhekiki msisitizu waki kwa ngangachu yela yeakahengiki Yesu, na ngacheakalembiki ghamaheli kubhokana na mbwaghu ya milenganesu jeakabhohiki Yesu. Mambu ghangi ghaghapalika nakanope ngati Yesu Kubatizwa, na kulengakeka kwaki kulipololu kola ngacheghalembakiki mu Injili jenu. 
\iot Ghaghabhihomu 
\io1 Yohana atumbula Injili mu, (Sula ja 1:1-18). 
\io1 Kabhete alemba kubhokana na ngangachu yakumu yeakahengiki Yesu, (Sula 1:19-12:50). 
\io1 Kubhokela panihapa alongela mambu ghamaheli gha matamu ghaka Yesu, ghaghapelakela nyiwa jaki na kuhyoka kwaki, (Sula 13:1-20:31). 
\io1 Yohana ajomulela Injili jaki mu, (Sula ja 21), akalongalya chikahi chimu Yesu paakabhapitalile bhandu baada ja kuhyoka kwaki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa, na bhela kulongela ndandi jaki ja kuchilemba chitabu chenu. 
\c 1  
\s1 Lilobhi akatendakiki Mundu 
\p  
\v 1 Mangani ja hindu yokapi kubhombakeka, kukabhi na Lilobhi, na Lilobhi hoju akabhi na Chapanga, najombi Lilobhi akabhi Chapanga.  
\v 2 Pakutumbula hapa Lilobhi hoju akabhi kwaka Chapanga.  
\v 3 Kupetela jombi Chapanga akabhombiki hindu yokapi, wala panga jombi nga chindu chokapi chechabhombakiki ambachu chibhombakike.  
\v 4 Jombi akabhi nde kutumbula kwa womi, na womi hoghu uletiki unang'anu wa bhandu.  
\v 5 Unang'anu hoghu ung'anya mulwihi, nalombi lwihi ngapalwaweziki kuluchuchuha. 
\p  
\v 6 Chapanga akuntumiki mundu jumu, lihina laki Yohana.  
\v 7 Akahikiki kubhapwaghi bhandu panani ja Unang'anu hoghu, nahuli kwa kupetela jombi bhandu bhokapi bhapata kujowana ulandilu waki na kuhobhalela.  
\v 8 Yohana mweni ngacheakabhi Unang'anu hoghu, nambu akahikiki kubhalandi bhandu panani ja Unang'anu hoghu.  
\v 9 Aghoghu nde Unang'anu wa chakaka, Unang'anu ghouhika pani pundema na kubhamulaki bhandu bhokapi. 
\p  
\v 10 Bhela Lilobhi jola akabhi pani pundema, na kwa kupetela jombi Chapanga akabhombiki ndema, nambu bhandu bha pundema ngachebhummanye.  
\v 11 Akahikiki kwa bhandu bhaki mweni, nambu bhombi ngachebhunjopalile.  
\v 12 Nambu bhokapi bhabhunjopalile na kunhobhalela, akabhapeki uwezu wa kuhengakeka bhana bhaka Chapanga, nde bhala bhabhalihobhalela lihina lake,  
\v 13 bhahengakiki bhana bhaka Chapanga nga kwa kubhelakeka ngati mobhabhelakake bhandu, au kwa kupala kwaka mundu, nambu bhabhelakiki kubhokana na Chapanga mweni. 
\p  
\v 14 Lilobhi akabhi mundu, na akatami kwitu, na tepani tukauweni ulumbalilu waki, ulumbalilu ngati waka Mwana kanjika joahuma kwa Atati, atweli chihomu na chakaka. 
\p  
\v 15 Yohana akabhalandi bhandu malobhi ghake, akajamalili nakanopi, na kupwagha, “Hajoju nde jola jonumpwaghilaje, ‘Joahika munyuma jangu, nambu nde nkolongwa kumbeta nepane, ndandi jombi akabhi mangane ja kubhelekeka nepani.’ ” 
\p  
\v 16 Kubhokana na ukamilifu waki, tepani tabhokapi tujopali chihomu panani ja chihomu.  
\v 17 Maghambu Chapanga akabhohiki Shelia kwa indela jaka Musa, nambu chihomu chaka Chapanga na chakaka jikahikiki kwa indela jaka Yesu Kristo.  
\v 18 Nga mundu jokapi joambweni Chapanga mu chikahi chokapi chela ng'o, nambu Chapanga Mwana kanjika jaki, joabhi pachihimba cha Atati waki, jonihoju nde joatulangihe ntundu Chapanga moabhelile. 
\s1 Ulandilu waka Yohana Mbatizaji 
\r Matayo 3:1-12; Mako 1:1-8; Luka 3:1-18 
\p  
\v 19 Haghoghu nde ulandilu waka Yohana, chikahi bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude pabhakabhatumiki bhapenganyambiku na Bhalawi kuhuma ku Yelusalemu nahuli bhakundalukyaje, “Bho, wehapa wa nane?” 
\p  
\v 20 Yohana akajetakili, wala ngacheakaniki, akapwaghike, “Nepani nga Kristo.” 
\p  
\v 21 Bhakundalukile, “Bho, henu wehapa wa nane? Bho, wehapa le wa Eliya?” 
\p Yohana akabhayangike, “Nga nepane.” 
\p Bhakundaluki kabhete, “Bho, wehapa le wa Mlota waka Chapanga jola?” 
\p Akabhayangike, “Nga nepane.” 
\p  
\v 22 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, wehapa wa nane? Bho, ulilongale bhole panani jaku wamwete? Utupwaghilaje, nahuli tupata liyangu la kubhapelakela bhala bhabhatutumike.” 
\p  
\v 23 Yohana akabhayangiki na kupwagha, ngati moakapwaghi mlota Isaya, 
\q1 “Nepani nde sauti jaka mundu jejijamalila kulipololu, 
\q1 ‘Ndenganakyaje indela jaka Bambo!’ ” 
\p  
\v 24 Na bhandu bhala bhabhakatumakiki bhakabhi bhahumiki kwa Mafalisayo.  
\v 25 Bhakundaluki Yohana, “Ngati wehapa nga wa Kristo, au nga wa Eliya, wala nga wa Mlota waka Chapanga jola, bho, maghambu ki ubatiza?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yohana akabhayangiki, akapwaghaje, “Nepani numbatiza kwa machi, nambu pachilanda jinu ajemiki mundu jwanga mabhanganya kummanya.  
\v 27 Jombi nde joahika punyuma jangu, nepani ngachembalika hata kujibhopola mighoji ja magubasi ghake.”\fig Mundu joawati magubasi|alt="A person wearing sandals" src="05 Sandals.jpg" size="col" ref="1:27" \fig* 
\p  
\v 28 Mambu aghagha ghokapi ghakahengakiki ku muchi wa Besania, kwihi ja nkoka Yoludani, koakabhi Yohana abatiza. 
\s1 Yesu nde Mwanalimbeleli waka Chapanga 
\p  
\v 29 Chilabhu jaki, Yohana akumbweni Yesu akahikaje kwaki, akapwaghike, “Lingalyaje, hajoju nde Mwanalimbeleli waka Chapanga, joatola mahoku gha ndema!  
\v 30 Hajoju nde jola jonukupwaghili, ‘Anahika mundu punyuma jangu, joabhi nkolongwa kumbeta nepani, maghambu jombi akabhili mangane ja kubhelakeka nepane.’  
\v 31 Nepani namwete ngachenummanye, nambu nhikiki kubatiza kwa machi, nahuli bhandu bha Izilaeli bhapata kummanya jombi.” 
\p  
\v 32 Yohana akalandili ana, “Nakumbweni Roho Mhuhu akahelalaje kuhuma kunani kumahunde ngati ngunda, na kumetela panani jaki.  
\v 33 Nepani ngachenummanyike, nambu jola joandumiki kubatiza kwa machi, jonihoju akambwaghile, ‘Jola jowambonaje Roho akahelalaje na kutama panani jaki, jonihoju nde joabatiza kwa Roho Mhuhu.’  
\v 34 Yohana akapwaghiki, nepani mweni lijambu leniheli, na nandila chakaka kubha hajoju nde Mwana waka Chapanga.” 
\s1 Bhabhulwa bha kutumbula bhaka Yesu 
\p  
\v 35 Chilabhu jaki kabhete, Yohana akabhi ajemiki papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki bhabhele.  
\v 36 Paakumbweni Yesu akapetaje, akapwaghike, “Lingalyaje, hajoju nde Mwanalimbeleli waka Chapanga!” 
\p  
\v 37 Bhabhulwa bhabheli bhala bhakunjowini Yohana akalongilaje, bhakunjengali Yesu.  
\v 38 Yesu akang'anambwiki, na paakabhaweni bhabhulwa habha bhakunjengalyaje, akabhapwaghile, “Bho, mpala kike?” 
\p Bhakamuyangike, “Labi,” ndandi jaki, “Mbola,” bho, utama kwako? 
\p  
\v 39 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Muhikaje, nanamu anambonaje. Bhabhulwa habha bhakunjengalile, na kupabhona paatama, na bhakatami kwaki lichobha lela. Ndandi kukabhi ngati saa kumi pakamihi.” 
\p  
\v 40 Andulea, ndongu waka Simoni Petulu, akabhi jumu wa bhabheli bhala bhabhakunjowini Yohana akalongilaje ghanihagha, na kunjengalela Yesu.  
\v 41 Jonihoju akumbweni hoti Simoni, ndongu waki mweni, na akumpwaghile, “Tumbweni Masihi.” Ndandi jaki, “Kristo.”  
\v 42 Najombi akumpeliki Simoni kwaka Yesu. 
\p Najombi Yesu akundingalili, na kumpwaghila, “Wehapa wa Simoni, mwana waka Yohana, nanau anaulowakika Kefa.” Ndandi jaki kwa Kigiliki nde Petulu, au Liganga. 
\s1 Yesu abhaloha Filipo na Nathanaeli 
\p  
\v 43 Lichobha la kabheli laki Yesu akapaliki kujenda ku inchi ja Galilaya. Bhela akumbweni Filipo, na kumpwaghila, “Unyengalyaje!”  
\v 44 Filipo akabhi mundu wa kuhuma ku muchi wa Betisaida, mwenehi wa muchi ghobhatama Andulea na Petulu.  
\v 45 Filipo akumbweni Nathanaeli, na kumpwaghila, “Tumbweni jombi ambaju Musa akalembiki panani jaki mu chitabu cha Shelia, na ambaju bhalota bhaka Chapanga nabhombi bhakalembiki panani jaki. Nde Yesu, mwana waka Yusufu, kuhuma ku muchi wa Nazaleti.” 
\p  
\v 46 Nathanaeli akumpwaghi Filipo, “Bho, liwezikana bholi lilobhi lamboni lihuma ku Nazaleti?” 
\p Filipo akumpwaghile, “Uhika ulolaje.” 
\p  
\v 47 Bhela Yesu akumbweni Nathanaeli akahika kwaki, na kulongela malobhi ghaki, “Lingalyaje Mwizilaeli chakaka, ngacheabhi na upuhi mkati jake.” 
\p  
\v 48 Nathanaeli akumpwaghile, “Bho, upatiki bholi kumanya?” 
\p Yesu akamuyangiki, akapwaghaje, “Nakakuweni mangane Filipo ngacheakulohiki, paukabhi pahi ja nkongu wa mtini.” 
\p  
\v 49 Nathanaeli akamuyangike, “Mbola, wehapa wa Mwana waka Chapanga! Wehapa nde Unkolongwa wa Izilaeli!” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu akamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Bho, maghambu nakakupwaghi, nakakuweni pahi ja nkongu wa mtini, nde ndandi uhobhalela? Anaubhonaje mambu makolongwa nakanopi kupeta ghangane.”  
\v 51 Yesu akajendali kubhapwaghila, numpwaghila, “Chakaka, anambonaje kunani kumahunde kuhoghoka, na bhatumika bhaka Chapanga bhakahelalaje na kukwela panani jaka Mwana waka Mundu.” 
\c 2  
\s1 Ukwati ku muchi wa Kana 
\p  
\v 1 Na lichobha la katatu kukabhi na ukwati ku muchi wa Kana, ja ku Galilaya. Na mabhu waka Yesu akabhi konikola,  
\v 2 Yesu najombi akabhi bhunkokiki paukwati ghola papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki.  
\v 3 Chikahi divai pajajomwiki, mabhu waka Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ngachebhabhi na divai.” 
\p  
\v 4 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mbomba, bho, maghambu kiki umbwaghi malobhi aghagha nepane? Chenjenu nga chikahi chechipalika kwangu nepani kuhenga leniheli.” 
\p  
\v 5 Amabhu waka Yesu akabhapwaghi bhatumika, “Lokapi lenaampwaghilaje, mulihengaje.” 
\p  
\v 6 Bhela kukabhi na ihulu sita ya maganga, kila chimu chakabhi na ukolongwa wa kutama machi madebi ghabheli au ghatatu, nayombi ikabhekakiki konihoku ngati mowabheli ntetu wa Bhayahude wa kuligholola kwa ndandi ja kunjojabhe Chapanga.  
\v 7 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ntwelakya machi tuwe mwihulu heyi.” Nabhombi bhakatwelaki mbaka panani.  
\v 8 Akabhapwaghile, “Henu ntekaje, na mumpelakyaje nkolongwa wa ukwati.” Nabhombi bhakapeliki.  
\v 9 Najombi nkolongwa wa chilebhe cha ukwati paakaghaonjiki machi ghala ghakang'anambwiki kubha divai, panga na kumanya koghahumiki, nambu bhatumika bhakamanyiki, bhala bhabhatekiki machi ghala, nkolongwa wa ukwati jola akundohiki bambo ukwati,  
\v 10 akumpwaghile, “Kila mundu atumbu hoti kuandaa divai jambone, na bhandu anabhanywili nakanopi, bhaleta divai jangakunogha. Nambu wehapa ujibhekiki divai jamboni mbaka sajenu!” 
\p  
\v 11 Nginyulila jenjenu ja kutumbula akahengiki Yesu ku Kana ja ku Galilaya, na kulangiha ulumbalilu waki, na bhabhhulwa bhaki bhakunhobhalile. 
\p  
\v 12 Paghapetiki ghanigala Yesu akahelili mbaka ku Kapelenaumu, jombi na mabhu waki na bhalongu bhaki na bhabhulwa bhaki, bhakatemi konihoku kwa machobha machokope. 
\s1 Yesu ajenda pa liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga 
\r Matayo 21:12-13; Mako 11:15-17; Luka 19:45-46 
\p  
\v 13 Pasaka ja Bhayahude jakabhi jiheghalile, najombi Yesu akakweliki mbaka ku Yelusalemu.  
\v 14 Akapaweni pala pa liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga bhandu bhakahemalya ng'ombi, na mambeleli, na ngunda na bhabhang'anambu mbija bhatami pameza yabhu.\fig Mundu joang'anambu mbija|alt="A business person who exchanges money" src="10 Money Changer.jpg" size="col" ref="2:14" \fig* 
\v 15 Akalokiki ntibhi kubha chiboku, akabhabhohiki bhokapi pa liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, na mambeleli na ng'ombi, akajitili mbija ya bhabhang'anambu mbija, na kuipendula meza yabhu,  
\v 16 akabhapwaghi bhala bhabhahemalela ngunda, “Muhibhoha hindu hayeyi pambane, na ngamwajitenda nyumba ja Atati wangu kubha pandu pa kuhemela na kulombasela!”  
\v 17 Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakakombwiki kubha ilembakiki mu Malembu Mahuhu, “Wenga wa Chapanga, wihu wangu kwa nyumba jaku unyocha ngati moto!” 
\p  
\v 18 Henu Bhayahude bhakamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Bho, anautulangiha nginyulila bholi, nahuli kutulangiha kubha ubhi na lujiniku lwa kuhenga mambu ghangane?” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu akabhayangike, na kubhapwaghila, “Mjibhombulaje Nyumba jaka Chapanga hajeji, na nepani ananjengaje kwa machobha ghatatu.” 
\p  
\v 20 Bhela Bhayahude bhakapwaghike, “Nyumba jaka Chapanga hajeji jakachengakiki kwa hyaka alobaini na sita, bho, na wehapa anauchengaje kwa machobha ghatatu?” 
\p  
\v 21 Nambu jombi akapwagiki kwa nyumba ja hyegha jake.  
\v 22 Bhela Yesu paakayokiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa, bhabhulwa bhaki bhakakombwiki kubha akapwaghiki ghanihagha, bhakaghahobhalili Malembu Mahuhu ghala, na malobhi ghokapi ghaakalongi Yesu. 
\s1 Yesu amanyi mitima ja bhandu bhokapi 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu paakabhi ku Yelusalemu ku uwangalalu wa Pasaka, bhandu bhamaheli bhakunhobhali kubha jombi nde Masihi, pabhiweni nginyulila yaki yeakahengike.  
\v 24 Nambu Yesu ngacheabhahobhalile, kwa ndandi jombi akabhamanyiki bhokapi,  
\v 25 na ngacheakabhi na ndandi ja kupala mundu wa kundandila mambu gha bhandu, kwa ndandi jombi mweni akamanyiki ghaghabhi mkati ja mtima waka mundu. 
\c 3  
\s1 Nikodemu anjendela Yesu ikilu 
\p  
\v 1 Kukabhi na mundu jumu wa Mafalisayo, lihina laki Nikodemu, jumu wa ihongozi bha pachengu pa Bhayahude.  
\v 2 Lichobha limu ikilu Nikodemu akunjedi Yesu, na kumpwaghila, “Labi, tumanyi kubha wehapa nde wambola, uhumiki kwaka Chapanga, kwa ndandi nga mundu joaweza kutenda nginyulila hayeyi yewitenda wehapa, nambu Chapanga abhi papamu naku.” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu akamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Chakaka, nukupwaghila, mundu nangakubhelakeka mala ja kabhele, ngaawezi kuubhona Ukolongwa waka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 4 Nikodemu akampwaghile, “Bho, aweza bholi mundu kubhelakeka kabheti, koni asejike? Bho, aweza kujingi mulutumbu lwa mabhu waki mala ja kabheli na kubhelakeka?” 
\p  
\v 5 Yesu akayangike, “Nukupwaghi chakaka, mundu nangakubhelakeka kwa machi na kwa Roho Mhuhu, ngaawezi kujingila mu Ukolongwa waka Chapanga.  
\v 6 Mundu abhelakeka kihyegha kwa atati na mabhu, nambu chechibhelakiki kiroho nde Roho Mhuhu.  
\v 7 Ngawikangacha ndandi nukupwaghili, ‘Hipalika kubhelakeka mala ja kabhele.’  
\v 8 Mpongu upogha koupala, na kupogha kwaki ukujowana, nambu ngacheumanya kouhuma wala koujenda. Bhenibhela nde mokubhelela kwaka mundu jola joabhelakiki kwa Roho Mhuhu.” 
\p  
\v 9 Nikodemu akundaluki Yesu, “Bho, mambu haghagha ghawezikana bholi kubha?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu akamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Bho, wehapa ubhi wambola wa ku Izilaeli, na mambu haghagha ngacheughamanye?  
\v 11 Nukupwaghi chakaka kubha, lela letulimanya tulipwagha, na lela letuliweni tulilandila, kabheti ulandilu witu ngachemujetakela.  
\v 12 Ngati numpwaghili mambu gha pani pundema, wala ngachemuhobhalela, bho, mwiweza bholi kuhobhalela, ananumpwaghi mambu gha kunani kumahunde?  
\v 13 Nga mundu joapiti kunani kumahunde, nambu jombi joaheli kuhuma kunani kumahunde, yani, Mwana waka Mundu joatama kunani kumahunde.” 
\p  
\v 14 Na ngati Musa moakalikwehi lijoka la shaba punkongu kulipololu kola, najombi Mwana waka Mundu anakwehakika bhelabhela,  
\v 15 nahuli kila mundu joanhobhalela akubhaje na womi wa mileli muka jombi.  
\v 16 Maghambu kwa ntundu aghoghu Chapanga akaupaliki ndema, hata akumbohiki Mwana waki wa kanjika, nahuli kila mundu joanhobhalela ngayihobha, nambu akubhaje na womi wa mileli.  
\v 17 Kwa ndandi Chapanga ngacheakuntumiki Mwana waki pani pundema nahuli kubhatemula bhandu bha pundema, nambu bhandu bha pundema bhapata kukengalewa kwa indela jaka jombi. 
\p  
\v 18 Joanhobhale Mwana waka Chapanga ngacheatemuliwa, nambu jwangakunhobhalela ajomwi kutemuliwa, maghambu ngachealihobhalili lihina laka Mwana wa kanjika waka Chapanga.  
\v 19 Na ghongoni nde utemuliku: Kubha unang'anu uhikiki kwa bhandu bha pundema, na bhandu bhakapaliki lwihi kuliku unang'anu, maghambu matendu ghabhu ghakabhi mahakau.  
\v 20 Ndandi kila mundu joatenda mahakau auhakalila unang'anu, wala ngacheahika mu unang'anu, nahuli matendu ghaki ngaghihika kulakaliwa.  
\v 21 Nambu jola joatenda gha chakaka ahika mu unang'anu, nahuli matendu ghaki ghabhonikanaje hotuhotu kubha ghahengakiki muka Chapanga. 
\s1 Yesu na Yohana Mbatizaji 
\p  
\v 22 Paghajomwiki ghanihagha Yesu na bhabhulwa bhaki bhakapiti mbaka ku inchi ja ku Yudea, akapilaki konihoku papamu nabhu, na kubatiza bhandu.  
\v 23 Yohana akabhi akabatiza bhandu ku Ainoni, pambipi na Salimu, kwa ndandi konihoku kukabhi na machi ghamaheli, na bhandu bhakunjendile, nabhombi bhakabatizwi.  
\v 24 Haghagha ghakahengakiki chikahi Yohana paakabhi akali ngacheabhekakiki muchifungo. 
\p  
\v 25 Bhela kukapitali kulochana kwa bhabhulwa bhaka Yohana na Myahude jumu panani ja ntetu wa kuligholola kwa ndandi ja kunjojabhe Chapanga.  
\v 26 Bhakunjendi Yohana, na kumpwaghila, “Mbola, jombi joakabhi papamu na wehapa kwihi ja Yoludani, jola joukamlandile malobhi ghaki, lingalyaje, sajenu atenda kubatiza, na bhandu bhokapi bhunjende jombi.” 
\p  
\v 27 Yohana akayangiki, na kupwagha, “Ngacheaweza mundu kujopalela lilobhi lokapi lela, pangakubha apatiki kuhuma kunani kwaka Chapanga.  
\v 28 Mabhanganya mabheni mwabhalandilu bhangu kubha nakapwaghiki, ‘Nepani nga Kristo, nambu ndumakiki palongi jaki.’  
\v 29 Joabhi naku mabhu ukwati nde bambo ukwati, nambu nkochi waki bambo ukwati, jombi joajema na kunjowanela, ahekalela paajowana malobhi akalongila bambo ukwati. Bhenibhela nde chiheku changu mochikamilikila.  
\v 30 Bhela Yesu ipalika atopila nakanopi, nambu nepani mbunguwaje.” 
\s1 Jombi joahika kuhuma kunani kumahunde 
\p  
\v 31 Jombi joahika kuhuma kunani kumahunde, nde nkolongwa kupeta bhokapi. Jombi joabhi wa pani pundema, nde wa pundema, najombi apwagha mambu gha pundema. Nambu joahika kuhuma kunani kumahunde atawala panani ja ghokapi.  
\v 32 Ghala ghaaghaweni na kughajowana, nde ghaaghalandila, na nga mundu joajetakela ulandilu waki.  
\v 33 Jombi joajetakili ulandilu waki ammanyakisha kubha Chapanga nde chakaka.  
\v 34 Kwa ndandi jombi joatumakiki na Chapanga aghalonge malobhi ghaka Chapanga, ndandi Chapanga antwelakela Roho Mhuhu waki panga na chipemu.  
\v 35 Atati ampala Mwana, najombi ampeki hindu yokapi mumabhoku ghaki.  
\v 36 Joanhobhalela Mwana abhi na womi wa mileli, na jwangakunhobhalela Mwana ngaubhoni womi, nambu inyela jaka Chapanga anajuntamilaje panani jaki. 
\c 4  
\s1 Yesu na mbomba Msamalia 
\p  
\v 1 Mafalisayo bhakajowini kubha Yesu abhapata bhabhulwa bhamaheli kupeta Yohana, na kubhabatiza bhandu.  
\v 2 Nambu nga Yesu mweni joakabhi abatiza bhandu, nambu bhabhulwa bhaki,  
\v 3 Bhela Yesu paakajowini mambu ghanihagha akabhokiki ku inchi ja Yudea, na akakelawiki kabheti mbaka ku Galilaya.  
\v 4 Pamwanja ghonihoghu ikampaliki kupeta ku muchi wa Samalia. 
\p  
\v 5 Bhela akahikiki ku muchi wa ku Samalia, ghoulowakeka Sikali, pambipi na ngonda ghola Yakobo ghoakumpeki Yusufu mwana waki.  
\v 6 Na panihapa pakabhi na chilibha chaka Yakobo. Bhela Yesu, kwa ndandi akatondiki na mwanja waki, akatami pambipi na pachilibha pala. Kukabhi ngati saa sita ja muhi. 
\p  
\v 7 Bhela akahikiki mbomba Msamalia kuteka machi. Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mbekya machi ngunywaje.”  
\v 8 Kwa ndandi chikahi hechi bhabhulwa bhaka Yesu bhakapiti kumbwani kuheme chilebhe. 
\p  
\v 9 Bhela mbomba Msamalia jola akumpwaghi Yesu, “Bho, kubhi bholi wehapa wa Myahude kupala machi kwangu nepani, koni nepani nu mbomba Msamalia?” Maghambu Bhayahude ngachebhajongana na Bhasamalia hata pachokope. 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu akamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Ngati ukamanyiki chindu chela Chapanga cheapala kukupekeha, najombi nde nane joakupwaghila, ‘Mbekya machi ngunywaje,’ ukabya unjopiki jombi, najombi akabya akupekihi machi ghaghabhi ghomi.” 
\p  
\v 11 Mbomba jola akumpwaghile, “Bambo, ngacheubhi na chindu cha kutekela machi, na chilibha nde chilachu. Bho, ughapatiki kwaku machi ghanihagha ghaghabhi ghomi?  
\v 12 Bho, wehapa ubhi unkolongwa kupeta tati witu Yakobo, joakatupeki chilibha chenu, najombi akanywili machi ghaki, na bhana bhaki, na hinyama yaki?” 
\p  
\v 13 Yesu akamuyangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Kila joakunywa machi aghagha anaabhona nywita kabhete.  
\v 14 Nambu mundu jokapi joanakunywa machi ghala ghaananumpekya nepani ngaibhoni inywita mileli. Nambu machi ghala ghaananupekya anaghabya chemichemi ja machi mkati jaki, ghakajitikaje womi wa mileli.” 
\p  
\v 15 Mbomba jola akapwaghike, “Bambo, umbekya machi ghanihagha, nganibhona inywita kabhete, wala nganihika kabhete pambane kuteka machi.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Jendaje ukundoha ndomi waku, na uhika naku pambane.” 
\p  
\v 17 Mbomba jola akamuyangiki, na kupwagha, “Ngachemili na ndomi wangu.” 
\p Yesu akumpwaghile, “Uyangiki wichu, ngacheubhi na ndomi waku.  
\v 18 Kwa ndandi ubhi na akanalomi nhwanu, na mwanalomi joubhi naku sajenu nga ndomi wako, panihapa upwaghiki chakaka.” 
\p  
\v 19 Mbomba jola akumpwaghile, “Bambo, mona kubha wehepa wa mlota waka Chapanga.  
\v 20 Akahoko bhitu bhakabhi bhajojabhela pa chitombi achechi, nanamu mpwagha kubha ku Yelusalemu nde pandu pa chakaka pa kunjojabhela Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mbomba, unhobhalyaje chembwagha, machobha ghahika ambapu ngamwanjojabheli Atati pa chitombi achechi, wala ku Yelusalemu.  
\v 22 Mwenga Bhasamalia mkijojabhela changa kuchimanya, nambu tepani tujojabhela chetukimanya, maghambu ukengaleku uhuma kwa Bhayahude.  
\v 23 Nambu chikahi chihika, na chombi chihikike, ambapu bhajojabhela bha chakaka anabhunjojabya Atati mu Roho Mhuhu na mu chakaka. Kwa ndandi Atati abhalonda bhandu ngati bhanihaba bhunjojabyaje.  
\v 24 Chapanga nde Roho, na bhombi bhabhunjojabhe jombi ibhapalika kunjojabhela mu Roho Mhuhu na mu chakaka.” 
\p  
\v 25 Mbomba jola akumpwaghile, “Manyi kubha anahika Masihi, joalowakeka Kristo, najombi paanahikaje, jombi anaatuhyekulyaje mambu ghokapi.” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu akamuyangike, “Nepani nenongela na wehapa, nde Masihi.” 
\p  
\v 27 Panihapa bhakahikiki bhabhulwa bhaki, bhakakangichi ndandi Yesu akabhi alongela na mbomba, nambu njeta hata jumu joakapwaghike, “Bho, ulonda kike?” Au, kundalukila, “Bho, mbona ulongela na mbomba?” 
\p  
\v 28 Bhela mbomba jola akachilekiki chihulu chaki, na kujenda kumbwane, na kubhapwaghi bhandu,  
\v 29 “Muhikaje, mumbona mundu joambwaghi mambu ghokapi ghanhengike. Bho, iwezekana le kubha hajoju nde Kristo?”  
\v 30 Bhela bhandu bhakahumiki kumbwani, na bhakunjendili Yesu. 
\p  
\v 31 Kunyuma kola bhabhulwa bhakabhi bhundobha, bhakapwaghaje, “Mbola, ukula chilebhe!” 
\p  
\v 32 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nepani mi na chilebhe changa kuchimanya mwehapa.” 
\p  
\v 33 Bhela bhabhulwa bhaka Yesu bhakapwaghanile, “Bho, kubhi na mundu joandeti chilebhe?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chilebhi changu nde achechi, naghatendaje mapalu ghaki jola joandumike, na kujomola lihengu laki.  
\v 35 Bho, mwehapa ngachempwagha, ‘Jikona myehi nchechi, nde paghihika mahunu?’ Lingalyaje, nepani numpwaghila, nkwehaje mihu ghinu mujilingalya mighonda, kubha chilebhi mungonda chijomwi kukoma, na chibhi tayali kwa mahunu.  
\v 36 Na jombi joahuna ajopalela malepu ghaki, na kubhongana mahunu kwa ndandi ja womi wa mileli, nahuli jola joapanda na jola joahuna bhapata kuhekalela papamu.  
\v 37 Kwa ndandi panihapa lilobhi leniheli likubha chakaka kubha, ‘Jumu apanda, na jongi kuhuna.’  
\v 38 Nenga nakuntumiki mughahuna ghala ghanga kughahangajakila, bhangi bhakahengiki lihengu lelinonwipe, nanamu mpatiki nyonjeka kubhokana na lihengu labhu lelinonwipe.” 
\p  
\v 39 Na ku muchi wa Bhasamalia ghola bhandu bhamaheli bhakunhobhali Yesu kwa ndandi ja kulandila kwaka mbomba jola, joakalandili kubha, “Akambwaghi mambu ghokapi ghanakahengike.”  
\v 40 Bhela Bhasamalia bhala pabhakunjendi Yesu, bhakundobhiki atama kwabhu, najombi akatami konikola machobha ghabhele. 
\p  
\v 41 Bhandu bhamaheli nakanopi bhakahobhalili kwa ndandi ja malobhi ghaka Yesu.  
\v 42 Bhakumpwaghi mbomba jola, “Henu tuhobhalela, wala nga kwa ndandi ja malobhi ghaku pela, maghambu tepani tujowini tabhete, na tumanyi kubha chakaka hajoju nde Kristo, Mkengalela wa ndema.” 
\s1 Yesu andamiha mwana waka Ofisa 
\p  
\v 43 Bhela paghapetiki machobha ghabheli hagha Yesu akabhokiki konihoku, na kujenda ku Galilaya.  
\v 44 Kwa ndandi Yesu mweni akapwaghiki, “Mlota waka Chapanga ngacheapata utopelu mu inchi jaki mwene.”  
\v 45 Bhela paakahikiki ku Galilaya, Bhagalilaya bhakunjopalili, kwa ndandi bhanganya habha na bhombi bhakapiti ku uwangalalu wa Pasaka, na bhakaghaweni mambu ghokapi Yesu ghaakahengiki ku Yelusalemu kola chikahi cha uwangalalu hoghu. 
\p  
\v 46 Bhela akahikiki kabheti ku Kana ja Galilaya, panihapa paakaghatendiki machi kubha divai. Panihapa pakabhi na ofisa jumu joakabhi na mwana waki mtamwa ku Kapelenaumu hoku.  
\v 47 Jombi paakajowini kubha Yesu ahikiki kuhuma ku Yudea mbaka ku Galilaya, akunjendili, akundobhiki ahelalaje na ajendaje kundamiha mwana waki joakabhi mtamwa, kwa ndandi akabhi pambipi kupotela.  
\v 48 Bhela Yesu akumpwaghile, “Nanga kubhona nginyulila na ngangachu, ngamwihobhaleli ng'o.” 
\p  
\v 49 Ofisa jola akumpwaghile, “Bambo, chondi uhelalaje mangani mwana wangu ngacheapotile.” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ujendaje, mwana waku alamike.” 
\p Mundu jola akalihobhali lilobhi lela leakalongi Yesu, najombi akapiti.  
\v 51 Na paakabhi ahelela, bhatumika bhaki bhakunjopalile, bhakapwaghaje, “Mwana waku alamike!” 
\p  
\v 52 Bhela akabhalalukili lisaa paakatumbwi kubha wichu, na bhombi bhakumpwaghili, “Lichu, saa saba ja muhi, chitamu chakundekike.”  
\v 53 Bhela tati waki akamanyiki kubha lisaa lelalela leakumpwaghi Yesu, “Mwana waku alamike.” Jombi na bhokapi bha munyumba jaki bhakunhobhali Yesu. 
\p  
\v 54 Jeniheji nde nginyulila ja kabheli jeakahengiki Yesu, paakabhi ahuma ku Yudea kujenda ku Galilaya. 
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu alamiha pa litanda la machi 
\p  
\v 1 Paghapetiki ghanihagha kukabhi na uwangalalu ghongi wa Bhayahude, najombi Yesu akakweliki kujenda ku Yelusalemu.  
\v 2 Na ku Yelusalemu hoku pundyangu ukolongwa wa muchi ghoulowakeka Ndyangu wa Limbeleli, pambipi jaki pakabhi na litanda la machi lelilowakeka kwa Kiebulania Betizata, nalombi lakabhi na mabalaza nhwanu.  
\v 3 Mkati ja mabalaza hagha kukabhi na lipogha likolongwa la bhatamwa bhaghonile, akangalola, iwete, na bhabhatengwike, bhakabhi bhalendalela machi ghakilabhanwaje.  
\v 4 Kwa ndandi kubhi chikahi cheahele mtumika wa kunani kwaka Chapanga, na kujingi mkati ja machi, na kughakilabhana machi. Bhela jola joakubha wa kutumbula kujibhila chikahi machi paghakilabhanwa, alama chitamu chokapi cheakabhi apatike.  
\v 5 Na panihapa pakabhi na mundu jumu, joakabhi atengwike kwa hyaka selasini na nane.  
\v 6 Yesu paakumbweni jonihoju aghonile, najombi akamanya kubha jombi abhi mtamwa na hali jeniheji kwa chikahi chilachu, akundalukile, “Bho, upala kulama?” 
\p  
\v 7 Mtamwa jola akamuyangiki, “Bambo, nepani ngachemi na mundu wa kumbeleka mulitanda, machi paghakilabhanwa, nambu chikahi panhika nepani, mundu jongi ajingila mangani jangu.” 
\p  
\v 8 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Jemaje, utola uleli waku, na ujendaje.”  
\v 9 Palapala mundu jola akalamike, na akalitwekiki uleli waki, na kujenda. 
\p Na lichobha leniheli lakabhi Lichobha la Sabato.  
\v 10 Kwa ndandi jeniheji Bhayahude bhakumpwaghi mundu joakalamishwi jola, “Lalenu nde Lichobha la Sabato, shelia jikanakila kutotola uleli waku.” 
\p  
\v 11 Jombi akabhayangike, “Jombi joandendiki mya mwomi nde joambwaghile, ‘Utola uleli waku, na ujendaje.’ ” 
\p  
\v 12 Bhela bhakundalukile, “Bho, joakupwaghi wehapa ulitweka uleli waku, na ujendaje, nde nane?” 
\p  
\v 13 Nambu mundu joakalamiki jola ngacheamanyiki joandamihe, ndandi Yesu akabhi ajomwi kubhoka, kwa ndandi pakabhi na bhandu bhamaheli pandu panipala. 
\p  
\v 14 Paghapetiki ghanihagha Yesu akunketanili mundu jola joakundamihe mkati ja Nyumba jaka Chapanga, akumpwaghile, “Ulingalyaje, ubhi wa mwomi, ngawihenga mahoku kabhete, ngalihika kukupata lijambu lihakau nakanopi.” 
\p  
\v 15 Mundu jola akapiti, akabhapwaghi malobhi bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude kubha Yesu nde joandamihe.  
\v 16 Kwa ndandi jeniheji Bhayahude bhakatumbwi kung'aha Yesu, kwa ndandi akahengiki mambu ghanihagha mu Lichobha la Sabato.  
\v 17 Yesu akabhayangiki, “Atati wangu ahenga lihengu mbaka sajenu, na nepani bhelabhela nhenga lihengu.” 
\p  
\v 18 Bhela kwa ndandi jeniheji bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhakajendali kulonda mbekenyu ja kunkoma, nga kwa ndandi akahekiti shelia ja Lichobha la Sabato pela, nambu papamu na ghanihagha akundohiki Chapanga Atati waki, na bhela kulitenda jombi alengana na Chapanga. 
\s1 Lujiniku lwaka Mwana waka Chapanga 
\p  
\v 19 Bhela Yesu akabhayangiki, na kubhapwaghila, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, Mwana ngacheaweza kuhenga lijambu lokapi lela kanjika jaki, nambu ahenga lijambu lela leambona Atati waki akahengaje, kwa ndandi ghokapi ghaahenga Atati, na Mwana najombi aghahenga ghaghagha.  
\v 20 Kwa ndandi Atati ampala Mwana, najombi andangiha ghokapi ghaahenga mweni. Hata mahengu makolongwa nakanopi kupeta ghanihagha anaandangihaje, nahuli mwehapa mpata kukangacha.  
\v 21 Ndandi ngati Atati moabhayoke bhakuwa na kubhapeke womi kabhete, bhelabhela na Mwana najombi abhapekeha womi bhala bhaabhapala.  
\v 22 Kabheti Atati ngacheantemu mundu jokapi, nambu ampeki Mwana lihengu la kubhatemula bhandu bhokapi,  
\v 23 nahuli bhandu bhokapi bhuntopila Mwana, ngati mobhuntopale Atati. Jokapi jwangakuntopela Mwana ngacheantopela Atati joantumike.” 
\p  
\v 24 Chakaka, numpwaghila, “Jombi joalijowana lilobhi langu na kunhobhalela jola joandumike abhi na womi wa mileli. Na wala ngaitemuliwe, nambu apetiki kuhuma mu kupotela na kujingila mu womi.  
\v 25 Chakaka, numpwaghila, lisaa lihika, na sajenu libhile, bhakuwa pabhijowanaje sauti jaka Mwana waka Chapanga, na bhala bhabhijowanaje anabhakubha bhome.  
\v 26 Ndandi ngati bhela Atati moabheli na womi mkati jaki, bhelabhela akumpeki na Mwana uwezu wa kubha na womi mkati jaki.  
\v 27 Na jombi akumpeki lujiniku lwa kutemula kwa ndandi jombi nde Mwana waka Mundu.  
\v 28 Ngamwikangacha malobhi ghanihagha, kwa ndandi lisaa lihika, ambalu bhokapi bhabhabhi mumatengeli anabhajowanaje sauti jaki.  
\v 29 Na bhombi anabhayokaje, bhala bhabhatehi manyahi kwa uyohakeku wa womi, na bhala bhabhatehi mahakau kwa uyohakeku wa utemulo.” 
\s1 Bhalandilu bhaka Yesu 
\p  
\v 30 “Nepani ngachenhweza kuhenga lihengu namwete, ngati monyowanela kuhuma kwa Atati bhenibhela nde mondemulila, na utemulu wangu nde wa chakaka, kwa ndandi ngachenonda kuhenga ngati mombali nepane, nambu ngati moapali jola joandumike.” 
\p  
\v 31 Nepani ngati ananililandi namwete, ulilandilu wangu nga wa chakaka.  
\v 32 Abhi jongi joanandila nepani, nanatu manyi kubha ulandilu waki ghoanandila nepani nde wa chakaka.  
\v 33 Mabhanganya mkabhatumiki bhandu kwaka Yohana Mbatizaji, najombi akundandili chakaka.  
\v 34 Nepani nga ngati nujopalela ulandilu wa bhandu, nambu nongela mambu aghagha nahuli mwehapa mpata kukengalewa.  
\v 35 Yohana akabhi ngati taa jejibhelela na kung'anya, nanamu mkahawi kuuhekalela unang'anu waki kwa chikahi.  
\v 36 Nambu ulandilu ghominaku nepani nde ukolongwa kupeta ghola waka Yohana, kwa ndandi mahengu ghala ghaambeki Atati nahuli naghajomulaje, mahengu ghanihagha ghanaghahenga, ghanandila kubha Atati nde joandumike.  
\v 37 Atati joandumike bhelabhela anandila. Sauti jaki ngachemujijowine chikahi chokapi, wala ngachemumbweni pamihu jaki.  
\v 38 Wala lilobhi laki ngachembinalu likatama mkati jinu, kwa ndandi mabhanganya ngachemunhobhalela jola joatumakiki na jombe.  
\v 39 Mughachunguzaje Malembelu Mahuhu, maghambu kwa ghanihagha mwehapa muholakela kubha mkati jaki mbi na womi wa mileli, na Malembu ghanihagha nde ghaghanandila nepane.  
\v 40 Wala ngachempala kuhika kwangu nepane, nahuli mpata kubha na womi wa mileli. 
\p  
\v 41 “Nepani ngachenulonda ulumbalilu kuhuma kwa bhandu.  
\v 42 Nambu nummanyiki mabhanganya kubha ngachembi na upalu waka Chapanga mkati ja mitima jinu.  
\v 43 Nepani nhikiki kwa lujiniku lwa Atati wangu, wala mabhanganya ngachemnyopalela, jongi anahikiki kwa lihina laki mwene, anamunjopalya jonihoju.  
\v 44 Bho, muweza bhole kuhobhalela mabhanganya mwenjopalanela ulumbalilu mabheni kwa mabheni, na ulumbalilu ghola ghouhuma kwaka Chapanga joabhi wa kanjika ngachemulonda?  
\v 45 Ngamwiholake nepani ananuntakila kwa Atati. Musa jomunhobhalela mabhanganya nde joantakila.  
\v 46 Kwa ndandi ngati mkabhili munhobhalela Musa, mkabya mnihobhalili na nepane, maghambu Musa akalembiki malobhi ghangu nepane.  
\v 47 Nambu ngati ngachemughahobhalela malembu ghaka Musa, bho, anamughahobhalya bhole mabholu ghangu nepane?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Yesu abhapeke chilebhi bhandu elufu nhwano 
\r Matayo 14:13-21; Mako 6:30-44; Luka 9:10-17 
\p  
\v 1 Paakajomwi ghanihagha Yesu akalombwiki kwihi ja Bahali ja Galilaya, au ghoulowakeka Bahali ja Tibelia.  
\v 2 Na lipgha likolongwa la bhandu lakunjengalile, kwa ndandi bhakaiweni ngangachu yeakabhahengi bhatamwa.  
\v 3 Bhela Yesu akakweliki kuchitombi, na akatami konihoku papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki.  
\v 4 Na chikahi cha uwangalalu wa Pasaka ja Bhayahude, chakabhi chiheghalile.  
\v 5 Bhela Yesu paakalingalili, na kulibhona lipogha likolongwa la bhandu lihika kwaki, akumpwaghi Filipo, “Bho, tuhemala kwaku mabumunda, nahuli bhandu abhabha bhapata kula?”  
\v 6 Na leniheli akalongi nahuli kundenga Filipo, kwa ndandi akamanyiki mweni leanahengaje. 
\p  
\v 7 Filipo akamuyangike, “Mabumunda gha ipandi mia mbili ya madini gha feza ngaghabhajaghanile, hata ngati kila jumu wabhu anaapatiki chipandi kichokope.” 
\p  
\v 8 Jumu wa bhabhulwa bhaki joalowakeka Andulea, ndongu waka Simoni Petulu, akumpwaghile,  
\v 9 “Pambani abhi nkombu jumu, joabhi na mabumunda nhwano gha shaili, na homba ibheli. Bho, nambu hayeyi anaijaghanya kiki kwa bhandu bhamaheli ngati abhabha?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu akapwaghike, “Mwatamika bhandu pahi.” Na pandu pala pakabhi na manyonyoli ghamaheli. Bhela akanalomi bhakatami, ngati bhandu elufu nhwano jumula jabhu.  
\v 11 Bhela Yesu akaghatoliki mabumunda ghala, akunchengwi Chapanga, na kubhapekeha bhabhulwa bhaki, na bhabhulwa bhakabhaghabhi bhandu bhabhakabhi bhatami, bhelabhela na homba yela kulengana na mobhapalilaje.  
\v 12 Na bhandu bhokapi pabhakatupile, akabhapwaghi bhabhulwa bhaki, “Mbonganaje ipandi yeihighalile, ngachihobha chokapi.”  
\v 13 Bhela bhakaibhongini papamu, na kutwelakela itonga komi na ibhele kubhokana na mabumunda nhwanu gha shaili ghala, ghabhakahighakile bhandu bhala bhabhakulike. 
\p  
\v 14 Bhela bhandu bhala, pabhajiweni nginyulila jeakahengiki Yesu, bhakapwaghike, “Chakaka hajoju nde Mlota waka Chapanga jola joakapwaghiki anahika pani pundema.”  
\v 15 Bhela Yesu paakamanyiki kubha bhakapaliki kuhika kunkamula kwa makili, nahuli bhumbeka kubha Nkolongwa wabhu, akabhokiki kabhete, na kujenda kuchitombi jombi kanjika jaki. 
\s1 Yesu ajenda panani ja machi 
\r Matayo 14:22-33; Mako 6:45-52 
\p  
\v 16 Hata pakwabhi pakamihi bhabhulwa bhaka Yesu bhakahelili ku bahali,  
\v 17 bhakakweliki mu liboti, na kutumbula kulomboka bahali kujenda ku Kapelenaumu. Chikahi hechi kukabhi lwihi lujingile, na Yesu akabhi akali ngakubhahikila.  
\v 18 Bahali jakatumbwi kuhakula kwa kupogha mpongu ukolongwa.  
\v 19 Bhela pabhakabhi bhahughiki ingahe na kujenda utali wa kilometa nhwanu au sita, bhakumbweni Yesu akajendaje panani ja machi na kuliheghalela liboti, bhakajowipi namaa.  
\v 20 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nde nepane, ngamwijoghopa!”  
\v 21 Bhela bhakapaliki kuntola Yesu mu liboti, na chikahi chelachela liboti lakahikiki mumaheku ja kobhakabhi bhajenda. 
\s1 Bhandu bhundonda Yesu 
\p  
\v 22 Chilabhu jaki lipogha la bhandu lelajemiki kwihi ja bahali bhakaweni kubha njeta liboti lengi konihoku nambu liboti limu pela, na bhakamanyiki kubha Yesu ngacheakajingi mu liboti lela papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki, nambu bhabhulwa bhaki bhakapiti kanjika jabhu.  
\v 23 Nambu ghakahikiki maboti ghangi kuhuma ku Tibelia mbaka pambipi na pandu pala lipogha likolongwa la bhandu pabhakulikaje mabumunda, chikahi Bambo paakunchengwi Chapanga.  
\v 24 Bhela lipogha la bhandu palaweni kubha Yesu ngacheabhi konihoku wala bhabhulwa bhaki, bhakajingili mu maboti ghangi bheni, na kujenda ku Kapelenaumu nahuli kundonda Yesu. 
\s1 Yesu nde libumunda la womi 
\p  
\v 25 Hata pabhakunhimanili kwihi ja bahali, bhakundalukile, “Mbola, wehapa uhikiki lile pambane?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu akabhayangiki, na kubhapwaghila, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, mwenga mnonda nepani nga kwa ndandi mkaweni nginyulila, nambu maghambu mkakuliki mabumunda ghala, na kutupila.  
\v 27 Ngamwachihenge lihengu chilebhi chechiyonangeka, nambu chilebhi chechitamakila mbaka womi wa mileli, ambachu Mwana waka Mundu anaampekyaje, kwa ndandi jonihoju nde joajeghaliki muhuli na Chapanga Atati.” 
\p  
\v 28 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, tutenda bholi nahuli tupata kughahenga mahengu ghaka Chapanga?” 
\p  
\v 29 Yesu akabhayangiki, na kubhapwaghila, “Haleli nde lihengu laka Chapanga, kubha munhobhalyaje jola joatumakiki najombi.” 
\p  
\v 30 Bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, anauhenga nginyulila bhole nahuli tujibhonaje na tupata kuhobhalela? Bho, anauhenga lihengu bhole?  
\v 31 Akahokolu bhitu bhakakuliki mana kulipololu ngati moilembakike mu Malembelu Mahuhu, ‘Akabhapeki mana kuhuma kunani kumahunde nahuli bhakulaje.’ ” 
\p  
\v 32 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, nga Musa joakumpeki mabumunda kuhuma kunani kumahunde, nambu Chapanga Atati wangu nde joampekeha mwehapa mabumunda gha chakaka kuhuma kunani kumahunde.  
\v 33 Kwa ndandi libumunda laka Chapanga nde jola joahelela kuhuma kunani kumahunde, na kuupekeha ndema womi.” 
\p  
\v 34 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bambo, machobha ghokapi utupekyaje libumunda leniheli.” 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nepani nde libumunda la womi. Jokapi joahika kwangu nepani ngayibhoni injala ng'o, na jola joanhobhale nepani ngayibhoni inywita ng'o.  
\v 36 Nambu numpwaghile kubha, njomwi kumona, nambu mwakali ngachemuhobhalela.  
\v 37 Bhokapi bhaambeke Atati anabhahika kwangu, kabheti jokapi joahika kwangu nganundekeli kunja ng'o.  
\v 38 Kwa ndandi ngachenheli kuhuma kunani kumahunde nahuli kuhenga ngati mombali nepani, nambu nhenga mapalu ghaka jola joandumike.  
\v 39 Na mapalu ghaka jola joandumike nde aghagha, ja kubha kwa bhokapi bhaambekihe nganunhoa hata jumu, nambu nimuyoha kabhete mu lichobha la kujomukela.  
\v 40 Kwa ndandi mapalu gha Atati wangu nde aghagha, ja kubha kila joandingalila Mwana na kunhobhalela jombi, akubhaje na womi wa mileli, na nepani ananimuyohaje mu lichobha la kujomukela.” 
\p  
\v 41 Bhela Bhayahude bhakutumbwi kung'ong'uteka, kwa ndandi akapwaghiki, “Nepani nde libumunda lelihelile kuhuma kunani kunahundi.”  
\v 42 Bhakapwaghike, “Bho, hajoju le nga Yesu, mwana waka Yusufu, jotummanyi atati waki na mabhu waki? Bho, henu apwagha bhole kubha, ‘Nhelili kuhuma kunani kumahunde?’ ” 
\p  
\v 43 Bhela Yesu akayangiki, na kubhapwaghila, “Ngamwing'ong'uteka mabheti kwa mabheti.”  
\v 44 Nga mundu joaweza kuhika kwangu nepani, nangakuhutwa na Atati joandumike, na nepani ananimuyohaje mu lichobha la kujomukela.  
\v 45 Ilembakiki mu Malembu gha bhalota bhaka Chapanga, “Bhandu bhokapi anabhabholakikaje na Chapanga.” Bhela kila mundu joanjowana Atati, na kulibhola kuhuma kwaki, jonihoju ahika kwangu nepani.  
\v 46 Njeta mundu joambweni Atati, nambu jombi joahuma kwaka Chapanga, jonihoju nde joambweni Atati.  
\v 47 Chakaka numpwaghila, jombi joanhobhalela nepani abhi na womi wa mileli.  
\v 48 Nepani nde libumunda la womi.  
\v 49 Akahokolu bhinu bhakakuliki mana kulipololu, na bhakapotile.  
\v 50 Nambu lendenu nde libumunda lelihelili kuhuma kunani kumahunde, na kubha mundu aweza kula, na wala ngayipotele.  
\v 51 Nepani nde libumunda lelihelili kuhuma kunani kumahunde, mundu anaakuliki libumunda lenu, anaatamaje mileli. Na libumunda lemoha nepani nde hyegha jangu, jenijibhoha kwa ndandi ja womi wa bhandu bha pundema. 
\p  
\v 52 Bhela Bhayahude bhakalochini bheni kwa bheni, bhakapwaghaje, “Bho, aweza bholi mundu ajoju kutupekeha tepani hyegha jaki nahuli tukulaje?” 
\p  
\v 53 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, ngati ngachemkula hyegha jaka Mwana waka Mundu, na kunywa mwahi waki, ngachembi na womi mkati jinu.  
\v 54 Joakula hyegha jangu, na kunywa mwahi wangu, abhi na womi wa mileli, na nepani ananimuyohaje mu lichobha la kujomukela.  
\v 55 Kwa ndandi hyegha jangu nde chilebhi cha chakaka, na mwahi wangu nde chakunywa cha chakaka.  
\v 56 Joakula hyegha jangu, na kunywa mwahi wangu, atama mkati jangu, na nepani ndama mkati jaki.  
\v 57 Ngati Atati joabhi mwome moandumi nepani, na nepani mili mwome kwa Atati, bhelabhela jola joangula nepani, anaakubha mwome kwangu nepani.  
\v 58 Lendenu nde libumunda lelihelile kuhuma kunani kumahunde, nga ngati akahokolu bhinu mobhakakuli mana, na kupotela, nambu jola joakula libumunda lendenu anaatamaje mileli.” 
\p  
\v 59 Yesu akapwaghiki malobhi ghanihagha paakabhi abhola mu nyumba ja kuhimanganila Bhayahude, ku Kapelenaumu hoku. 
\s1 Malobhi gha womi wa mileli 
\p  
\v 60 Bhela bhandu bhamaheli pachilanda ja bhabhulwa bhaki pabhakajowini lijambu leniheli, bhakapwaghike, “Mambu aghagha nde ghanonwipe, bho, mundu bholi joaweza kughajowanela?” 
\p  
\v 61 Najombi Yesu akamanyi muntima waki kubha bhabhulwa bhaki bhaling'ong'utakela lijambu leniheli, akabhapwaghile, “Bho, lijambu haleli le luntenda kuhakalila?  
\v 62 Bho, henu anakukubha bhole pamwambona Mwana waka Mundu akagholukaje kujenda kola koakabhi pakutumbula?  
\v 63 Roho Mhuhu nde joajeghela womi, hyegha jaka mundu ngachejibhi na chindu ndeka. Nambu malobhi ghanihagha ghanumpwaghile nde Roho, kabheti nde womi.  
\v 64 Nambu kubhi na bhangi pachilanda jinu bhangakuhobhalela.” Kwa ndandi Yesu akamanyiki kutumbu pa kutumbulila kubha nde bhangakuhobhalela, najombi nde nane joamung'anambukaje.  
\v 65 Akapwaghike, “Kwa ndandi jeniheji nukumpwaghili kubha nga mundu joaweza kuhika kwangu nepani, pangakujangatiwa na Atati wangu.” 
\p  
\v 66 Kwa ndandi ja ghanihagha bhamaheli pachilanda ja bhabhulwa bhaki bhakakelawiki kunyuma, na ngachebhalongini naku kabhete.  
\v 67 Bhela Yesu akabhalalukili bhabhulwa bhaki komi na bhabheli bhala, “Bho, mwehapa nanamu mpala kubhoka?” 
\p  
\v 68 Bhela Simoni Petulu akamuyangike, “Bombo, bho, tujenda kwaka nane? Wehapa ubhi na mabholu ghaghaleta womi wa mileli.  
\v 69 Na tepani tuhobhalela, kabheti tumanyi, ja kubha wehapa nde Kristo, Mhuhu waka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 70 Yesu akabhayangike, “Bho, nepani ngachenunhawili mwenga komi na bhabheli, na jumu winu nde Shetani?”  
\v 71 Panihapa Yesu akabhi andongalela Yuda, mwana waka Simoni Isikalioti, ndandi jonihoju nde joamung'anambukaje, najombi nde jumu wa bhabhulwa komi na bhabheli bhala. 
\c 7  
\s1 Yesu na bhalongu bhaki 
\p  
\v 1 Paghajomwiki ghanihagha Yesu akabhi ajenda mu Galilaya, ndandi ngacheapaliki kujenda mu Yudea, kwa ndandi bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhakabhi bhalonda kunkoma.  
\v 2 Na chikahi cha uwangalalu wa Bhayahude, Uwangalalu wa Indamba, chakabhi chiheghalile.  
\v 3 Bhela bhalongu bhaka Yesu bhakumpwaghile, “Ubhoka pambane, na ujenda ku Yudea, nahuli bhabhulwa bhaku nabhombi bhapata kughabhona mahengu ghaku ghaughahenga.  
\v 4 Nga mundu joatenda mambu kwa kulihiya, na koni mweni apala kumanyikana. Ngati anauhenga mambu aghagha, bhela ulilangihaje wamwete pundema wokapi.”  
\v 5 Kwa ndandi hata bhalongu bhaki ngachebhunhobhalile. 
\p  
\v 6 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chenjenu nga chikahi changu chechipalika, nambu kwinu mwehapa chikahi chokapi chipalika.  
\v 7 Bhandu bha pundema ngabhawezi kunhakalila mwehapa, nambu bhanhakalila nepani, kwa ndandi nepani nabhalandila kubha matendu ghabhu nde mahakau.  
\v 8 Nkwelaje mwehapa njendanyaje mkakula uwangalalu. Nepani nga ngweli nakona kujenda kula uwangalalu hoghu, kwa ndandi chikahi changu chekimbalila chakali ngachechihikike.”  
\v 9 Paakajomwi kubhapwaghi malobhi ghanihagha, akajendali kutama mu Galilaya. 
\s1 Yesu ku Uwangalalu wa Indamba 
\p  
\v 10 Hata bhalongu bhaki pabhajomwili kukwela kujenda ku Uwangalalu wa Indamba, na Yesu akakweliki kujenda ku uwangalalu, nga kwa kubhonikana, nambu ngati kwa kulihiya.  
\v 11 Bhela bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhakundondiki pa uwangalalu, bhakapwaghaje, “Bho, abhi kwako mundu jola?” 
\p  
\v 12 Kukabhi na kujojalanela kwamaheli pa lipogha la bhandu panani jaki jombi. Na bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Mundu hoju nde wambone.” Bhandu bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Ngabhela, nambu abhakolowa bhandu.”  
\v 13 Nambu nga mundu joakumpwaghiki Yesu palanga, kwa ndandi ja kubhajoghopa bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude. 
\p  
\v 14 Pajahika pakati ja uwangalalu Yesu akakweliki na kujingila mu liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, na kutumbula kubhola.  
\v 15 Bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhakakangichi bhakapwaghaje, “Bho, mundu ajoju apatiki bhole kumanya mambu aghagha, koni ngacheasomike?” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhela Yesu akabhayangiki, na kupwagha, “Mabholu ghangu nga ghangu namwete, nambu ghaka jombi joandumike.  
\v 17 Mundu anaapaliki kughahenga mapalu ghaka Chapanga, anaamanyaje kubha mabholu ghangu ghahuma kwaka Chapanga, au nepani nongela kwa ndandi jangu namwete.  
\v 18 Jola joalongela kwa ndandi jaki mweni pela alonda lujiniku lwaki mweni. Nambu jola joalonda lujiniku lwaka jola joantumiki, jonihoju nde wa chakaka, na wala mkati jaki njeta uhakau.  
\v 19 Bho, Musa ngacheakumpeki Shelia? Nambu njeta hata jumu winu joajikamula Shelia heji. Bho, maghambu kiki mpala kungoma?” 
\p  
\v 20 Bhandu bhakayangike, “Wehapa ubhi na majobhi! Bho, nane joapala kukukoma?” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu akabhayangike, “Nepani nakahengiki ngangachu jimu, na mwehapa mabhokapi mkangacha.  
\v 22 Musa akumpeki malaghalakilu gha jando, nambu nga ngati ghahuma kwaka Musa, nambu kwa akahokolu, nanamu munheketa mundu jandu hata mu Lichobha la Sabato.  
\v 23 Bhela ngati anakubhi mundu aheketa jandu hata mu Lichobha la Sabato nahuli Shelia jaka Musa ngajihika kuhekateka, bho, mbona muhyomela nepani kwa ndandi nakundamihi mundu mu Lichobha la Sabato?  
\v 24 Nkotukaje kutemula mambu kwa kulingalila kwa kunja pela, nambu mughalingaje mambu na kutemula kwa chakaka.” 
\s1 Bho, hajoju le nde Kristo? 
\p  
\v 25 Bhela bhandu bhakumu bha ku Yelusalemu bhakapwaghike, “Bho, hajoju le nga mundu jola ambaju ihongozi bhundonda nahuli bhunkomaje?”  
\v 26 Lingalyaje, abhi pambane! Akalongilaje palanga, wala ngachebhumpwaghi lilobhi lokapi lela. Bho, iwezikana kubha chakaka ihongozi abhabha bhamanyi kubha hajoju nde Kristo?  
\v 27 Nambu hajoju tummanyi koahuma, nambu Kristo paanahikaje, nga mundu joamanya koahuma. 
\p  
\v 28 Bhela Yesu akajamalili sauti jaki mu liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, akabholaje na kupwagha, “Bho, nepani mmanye, na konhuma hoku mkumanye? Wala nepani ngachenhikiki kwa ndandi ja lujiniku lwangu namwete, nambu jombi joandumike nde wa chakaka, jwangakummanya mwehapa.  
\v 29 Nambu nepani nummanyi jombi, kwa ndandi nhumiki kwaki, najombi nde joandumike.” 
\p  
\v 30 Bhela bhandu bhakalondiki kunkamula, nambu nga mundu joakahatambwili chiwoku chaki nahuli kunkamula, kwa ndandi lisaa laki lakabhi likali ngakuhika.  
\v 31 Bhandu bhamaheli pa uwangalalu pala bhakunhobhalile, na bhakapwaghike, “Bho, Kristo paanahikaje, anahenga nginyulila yamaheli nakanopi kupeta yeahengiki mundu ajojo?” 
\s1 Manjolinjoli bhatumakika kunkamula Yesu 
\p  
\v 32 Mafalisayo bhakabhajowini bhandu bhakang'ong'utikaje malobhi ghanihagha panani jaka Yesu, bhela bhapenganyambiku bhakolongwa papamu na Mafalisayo bhakabhatumiki bhalonda bha Nyumba jaka Chapanga nahuli bhakunkamulaje.  
\v 33 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nakona mili na mwehapa kwa chikahi kichokopi pela, na bhela ananyendaje kwaka jola joandumike.  
\v 34 Mwinonda nepani, wala ngamwimone, na nepani pamile mwehapa ngachemuweza kuhika.” 
\p  
\v 35 Bhela bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhakapwaghanile, “Bho, hajoju anajenda kwaku, hata tepani ngatumbona? Bho, apala kujenda ku michi ja Bhagiliki kobhaghabhaniki Bhayahude, na kubhabhola Bhagiliki?  
\v 36 Bho, nde lilobhi bhole leniheli lealilongile, ‘Anamunonda nambu ngamwimone, wala nepani pamile mwehapa ngamuwezi kuhika?’ ” 
\s1 Mikoka ja machi gha womi 
\p  
\v 37 Pa lichobha la kujomukela, lichobha lela likolongwa la uwangalalu, Yesu akajemiki, na kujamalila, akapwaghaje, “Mundu joabhona inywita, ahikaje kwangu nepani, na akunywaje.  
\v 38 Ngati moghapwaghi Malembu Mahuhu kubha, ‘Jola joanhobhalela nepani, mikoka ja machi ghaghabhi womi anajipitaje kuhuma mkati jaki.’ ”  
\v 39 Yesu akalilongi lilobhi leniheli kubhokana na Roho Mhuhu, ambaju bhala bhabhunhobhalela anabhunjopalyaje, kwa ndandi Roho Mhuhu akabhi akali ngakuhika, na maghambu Chapanga akabhi akali ngakuuyekula ulumbalilu waka Yesu. 
\s1 Kulekangana pachilanda ja bhandu 
\p  
\v 40 Bhela bhandu bhangi pa uhangalalu pala pabhakajowini malobhi ghanihagha, bhakapwaghike, “Chakaka hajoju nde jola Mlota waka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 41 Bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Hajoju nde Kristo.” 
\p Nambu bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Bho, Kristo aweza bhole kuhuma ku Galilaya?  
\v 42 Bho, Malembu Mahuhu ngacheghapwagha, ‘Kristo anahikaje kuhuma mu lubheleku lwaka Nkolongwa Daude, na kuhuma ku Beselehemu, na muchi ghola ghoatamika Daude?’ ”  
\v 43 Bhela kukapitali na kulekangana pachilanda ja lipogha la bhandu kwa ndandi jaka Yesu.  
\v 44 Bhakumu bhabhu bhakapaliki kunkamula, nambu nga mundu joakalengiki kuhatambula chiwoku chaki nahuli kunkamula. 
\s1 Kukotoka kuhobhalela kwa bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude 
\p  
\v 45 Bhela bhalonda bhala bhakabhajendili ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku na Mafalisayo. Nabhombi bhakabhapwaghile, “Bho, mbona ngachemundetiki Yesu?” 
\p  
\v 46 Bhalonda bhala bhakabhayangike, “Nga mundu jokapi joalabhali kulongela ngati mundu hajoju!” 
\p  
\v 47 Bhela Mafalisayo bhakabhayangike, “Bho, mwehapa nanamu atehi kunkolowa?  
\v 48 Bho, ndabhali le kumbona chiongozi jokapi jola wa Bhayahude joanhobhalela, au pachilanda ja Mafalisayo?  
\v 49 Ngabhela! Nambu bhandu abhabha bhangakujimanya Shelia jaka Musa bhabhili na masolu!” 
\p  
\v 50 Panihapa Nikodemu, jola joakabhi anjendili Yesu lichobha limu ikilu, ambaju akabhi jumu wabhu, akabhapwaghile,  
\v 51 “Bho, Shelia jitu juntemu mundu panga na kunjowanela hote, na kumanya cheahengike?” 
\p  
\v 52 Bhakamuyangike, na kumpwaghila, “Bho, wehapa nanau uhumiki ku Galilaya? Ulondaje na anaubhonaje kubha nga mlota waka Chapanga joahuma ku Galilaya.”  
\v 53 Bhela, kila jumu akabhujiki kunyumba jaki. 
\c 8  
\s1 Mbomba akamulika akahengaje ugone 
\p  
\v 1 Bhela Yesu akapiti mbaka ku Chitombi cha Mizeituni.  
\v 2 Lukela pakwachile akajingili kabheti mu liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, na bhandu bhokapi bhakunjendile, najombi akatami pahi, na kutumbula kubhabhola.  
\v 3 Bhabhola bha Shelia na Mafalisayo bhakundetili mbomba jumu joakamuliki akahenga ugone, na kunjemeka pachilanda jabhu,  
\v 4 bhakumpwaghi Yesu, “Mbola, mbomba hajoju akamuliki paakabhi ahenga ugone.  
\v 5 Bhela mu Shelia jitu, Musa akatulaghalakili kubhalapula kwa maganga mbaka bhapotilaje akambomba ngati abhabha. Nambu bho, wehapa upwagha bhole?”  
\v 6 Bhombi bhakapwaghiki lilobhi leniheli kwa kundenga Yesu, nahuli bhapataje ndandi ja kumtakila. Nambu Yesu akajinimi, na kulemba paluhombi, kwa lukonji lwaki. 
\p  
\v 7 Bhombi pabhakajendali kundalukila, akajinwiki, na kubhapwaghila, “Mundu jokapi jwangakubha na mahoku pachilanda jinu, na akubhaje wa kutumbula kundapula liganga.”  
\v 8 Akajinimi kabheti pahi na kulemba paluhombi.  
\v 9 Bhombi pabhajowini malobhi ghanihagha bhakatakilwi na zamili yabhu, na bhakabhokiki jumu jumu, bhakatumbula bhazee. Yesu akahighali kanjika jaki, na mbomba jola akabhi ajemiki palapala.  
\v 10 Yesu akajinwiki na kumpwaghila mbomba jola, “Mbomba, bho, bhabhi kwaku bhala bhabhakutakile? Bho, nga jumu joakutemwili kubha na lihoku?” 
\p  
\v 11 Mbomba jola akamuyangike, “Bambo, njeta hata mundu jumu.” 
\p Yesu akumpwaghile, “Wala nepani nganukutemule. Ujendaje, na kutumbu sajenu ngawihenga mahoku kabhete.” 
\s1 Yesu unang'anu wa ndema 
\p  
\v 12 Bhela Yesu akalongili na bhandu kabhete, akapwaghaje, “Nepani nde unang'anu wa ndema, jombi joanyengalela nepani ngaajendi mulwihi ng'o, nambu anakubhaje na unang'anu wa womi.” 
\p  
\v 13 Bhela Mafalisayo bhakumpwaghile, “Wehapa ulilandila wamwete, kulilandila kwaku nga kwa chakaka.” 
\p  
\v 14 Yesu akayangike, “Nepani hata ngati nililandila namwete, ulandilu wangu nde wa chakaka, kwa ndandi manyi konhuma, na kola konyenda. Nambu mwehapa ngachemmanyi kola konhuma, wala kola konyenda.  
\v 15 Mwehapa mtemula kwa kujengalela mambu gha hyegha, nambu nepani ngachenuntemula mundu jokapi jola.  
\v 16 Nepani hata ngati anandemwile, utemulu wangu nde chakaka. Kwa ndandi nepani ngachemi kanjika jangu, nambu mili nepani papamu na Atati joandumike.  
\v 17 Kabheti ilembakiki mu Shelia hinu kubha, ulandilu wa bhandu bhabeli nde wa chakaka.  
\v 18 Nepani nililandila namwete, najombi Atati joandumiki anandila bhelabhela.” 
\p  
\v 19 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, abhi kwaku Atati wako?” 
\p Yesu akabhayangike, “Nepani ngachemmanye, wala Atati wangu ngachemummanye. Ngati mkamanyiki nepani, mkabya mummanyiki na Atati wangu.” 
\p  
\v 20 Yesu akaghalongili malobhi ghanihagha paakabhi abhola mu liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, mu chumba cha kubheke masanduku gha nyambiko. Wala nga mundu joakunkamwile, kwa ndandi lisaa laki lakabhi likali ngakuhika. 
\s1 Yesu apwagha panani ja nyiwa jaki 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu akabhapwaghi kabhete, “Nepani ndenda kubhoka, nanamu anamnondaje, nanamu anampotilaje mu mahoku ghinu. Konyenda nepani, mwehapa ngamuwezi kuhika.” 
\p  
\v 22 Bhela ihongozi bha Bhayahude bhakapwaghike, “Bho, anaalikoma le mwene? Kwa ndandi apwagha, ‘Konyenda nepani, mwehapa ngamuwezi kuhika!’ ” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Mwehapa muhumiki pahi, nambu nepani nhumiki kunani kumahunde. Mwehapa nde bha pani pundema, nambu nepani nga wa pundema ghoni.  
\v 24 Bhela nakumpwaghi kubha anampotilaje mu mahoku ghinu, kwa ndandi nangakuhobhalela kubha, ‘Nepani nde Jombi,’ anampotilale mu mahoku ghinu.” 
\p  
\v 25 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, wehapa wa nane?” 
\p Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nepani nde jola jonakabhili nukumpwaghilaje kutumbu pakutumbula.  
\v 26 Mili naghu ghamaheli gha kulongela na kutemula panani jinu. Nambu jola joandumike nde chakaka, nanatu ghanaghajowini kwaki nde ghanongela kwa bhandu bha pundema.” 
\p  
\v 27 Wala ngachebhamanyi kubha akabhi abhapwaghila panani jaka Chapanga Atati wake.  
\v 28 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Pamwibya njomwili kunkweha panani Mwana waka Mundu, panihapa nde pamwimanyaje kubha ‘Nepani nde Jombi,’ na kubha ngachenhenga lilobhi lokapi lela ngati mombali namwete, nambu nongela chela pela ngati Atati wangu moamolile.  
\v 29 Jombi joandumike abhi papamu na nepani, Atati ngacheanekiki nepani kanjika jangu, kwa ndandi machobha ghokapi nhenga mambu ghala ghaghunyambiha.” 
\p  
\v 30 Yesu paakabhi alongela malobhi ghanihagha, bhandu bhamaheli bhakunhobhalile. 
\s1 Chakaka anajumbeka kulijeka 
\p  
\v 31 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghi Bhayahude bhabhunhobhali bhala kubha, “Mwehapa anamtamakili mu malobhi ghangu, anamkubhaje bhabhulwa bhangu bha chakaka.  
\v 32 Anamujimanya chakaka, na chakaka heji anajumbeka mwehapa kulijeka.” 
\p  
\v 33 Bhakamuyangike, “Tepani tubhi lubheleku lwaka Ibulahimu, wala ngachetubhi bhatumwa bhaka mundu jokapi jola. Bho, uweza bhole kupwagha kubha, ‘Anambya kulijeka?’ ” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu akabhayangike, “Chakaka numpwaghila, kila mundu joahenga mahoku nde mtumwa wa mahoku.  
\v 35 Wala mtumwa ngacheatama panyumba machobha ghokape, nambu mwana atama mileli.  
\v 36 Bhela ngati Mwana anaambekiki kulijeka, anambya kulijeka chakaka.  
\v 37 Manyi kubha mwehapa nde lubheleku lwaka Ibulahimu, nambu mpala kungoma, maghambu lilobhi langu ngachelibhi mkati jinu.  
\v 38 Ghanaghaweni kwa Atati wangu nde ghanaghalongela, nanamu bhelabhela ghamughajowini kwa atati winu nde ghamughahenga.” 
\p  
\v 39 Bhakayangike, “Atati witu nde Ibulahimu!” 
\p Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ngati mkabhi bhana bhaka Ibulahimu, mkabya mughahengiki mahengu ghala ghaakahengiki Ibulahimu.”  
\v 40 Nambu sajenu mpala kungoma nepani, nenumpwaghili jejibhi chakaka jenyowini kwaka Chapanga. Ibulahimu ngacheahengiki bhenibhela.  
\v 41 Mwehapa mughahenga mahengu gha atati winu. 
\p Bhombi bhakamuyangike, “Tepani ngachetwabhelakiki kwa ukemi, tepani tubhi na Atati jumu, yani, Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 42 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ngati Chapanga akabhi Atati winu, mkabya mbaliki nepani, kwa ndandi nakahumiki kwaka Chapanga, na sajenu mili pambane, wala ngachenahikiki kwa kupala namwete, nambu jombi nde joandumike.  
\v 43 Bho, mbona ngachemughamanya aghagha ghanumpwaghila? Nde kwa kubha mwehapa ngachempala kughajowanela mabholu ghangu.  
\v 44 Mwehapa nde mabhana bha atati winu Shetani, na mpala pe kuhenga matokulelu gha atati winu. Jombi akabhi wa kukoma bhandu kutumbu pamwandi, na wala ngacheakajemi mu upambala wa chakaka, na chakaka ngachejibhili mkati jake. Paalonge upuhe, alongela ghaghabhi ghaki mweni, kwa ndandi jombi nde mpuhe, na atati wa upuhe.  
\v 45 Kwa ndandi nepani numpwaghi chakaka, nambu mwehapa ngachemnihobhalela.  
\v 46 Bho, mundu bholi pachilanda jinu joaweza kulangiha kubha nepani mili na mahoku? Na ngati nongela chakaka, bho, mbona ngachemnihobhalela?  
\v 47 Jombi joabhi waka Chapanga aghajowana malobhi ghaka Chapanga, bhela mwehapa ngachenjowanela kwa ndandi mwehapa nga mabhandu bhaka Chapanga.” 
\s1 Yesu nde nkolongwa kupeta Ibulahimu 
\p  
\v 48 Bhayahude bhakamuyangiki Yesu, “Bho, tepani ngachetupwagha chakaka kubha wehapa nde Msamalia, na kabheti ubhi na lijobhe?” 
\p  
\v 49 Yesu akayangike, “Nepani ngachemi na lijobhe. Nepani nuntopela Atati wangu, na mwehapa muheketa utopelu wangu.  
\v 50 Nepani ngachenonda ulumbalilu wangu, nambu abhi jumu joanondela ulumbalilu wango.  
\v 51 Chakaka numpwaghila, mundu anaalikamwili lilobhi langu, ngayipoteli mileli.” 
\p  
\v 52 Bhela Bhayahude bhakumpwaghile, “Sajenu tumanyi kubha wehapa ubhi na lijobhe. Ibulahimu apotile, na bhalota bhaka Chapanga bhapotile, na wehapa upwagha kubha, ‘Mundu anaalikamwi lilobhi langu, ngayipoteli mileli.’  
\v 53 Bho, wehapa le unkolongwa kupeta atati witu Ibulahimu, ambaju apotile? Nabhombi bhalota bhaka Chapanga bhapotile. Bho, wehapa ulitenda kubha wa nane?” 
\p  
\v 54 Yesu akayangike, “Ananililumbalili namwete ulumbalilu wangu nga chindu. Joanumbali nepani nde Atati wangu, ambaju mwehapa mpwagha kubha nde Chapanga winu.  
\v 55 Wala mwehapa ngachemummanye, nambu nepani nummanye. Ngati anambwaghiki ngachenummanye, anangubha numpuhe ngati mwehapa. Nambu nummanye, na lilobhi laki nilikamula.  
\v 56 Atati winu, Ibulahimu, akahekalili kulibhona lichobha la kuhika kwangu, najombi akaliweni, na akahekalile.” 
\p  
\v 57 Bhela Bhayahude bhakumpwaghile, “Wehapa wakali ngacheuhikiki hyaka hamsini, bho, upwagha bhole kubha umbweni Ibulahimu?” 
\p  
\v 58 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, mangani jaka Ibulahimu kubhelakeka, ‘Nepani mile.’ ” 
\p  
\v 59 Bhela bhakatondwili maganga nahuli kundapula, nambu Yesu akalihiiki, na kupita pa Nyumba jaka Chapanga, na kubhoka. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yesu andamiha mundu joabhelakiki ngalola 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu paakabhi apeta, akumbweni mundu joakabhi ngalola kutumbu kubhelakeka.  
\v 2 Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakundalukili bhakapwaghaje, “Mbola, bho, nane joatendiki mahoku, mundu ajoju au bhabheleka bhaki, mbaka abhelakika ngalola?” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu akayangike, “Hajoju ngacheatendiki mahoku, wala bhabheleka bhaki, nambu akabhelakiki ngalola nahuli makili ghaka Chapanga ghabhonikanaje ghahenga lihengu mkati jaki.  
\v 4 Imbalika kuhenga mahengu ghaki jombi joandumike. Koni kwakali muhi, ikilu jihika, kwanga kuweza mundu kutenda lihengu.  
\v 5 Chikahi chemili pundema, nepani nde unang'anu wa ndema.” 
\p  
\v 6 Paakajomwi kulongela ghanihagha, Yesu akahuniki imata pahi, akatendiki litopi kwa imata ghala, na kumpaka ngalola jola litopi mumihu,  
\v 7 na kumpwaghila, “Ujendaje ukachamba machi ku litanda la Siloamu. Silohamu ndandi jaki joatumakike.” Bhela akapiti, na kuchamba machi, na kukelabhuka koni akabya alola. 
\p  
\v 8 Bhela bhandu bha pambipi jaki, na bhala bhabhakumbweni mwandi kubha akabhi njopajopa, bhakapwaghike, “Bho, hajoju le nga jola joakabhi akatamaje na kujopajopa?” 
\p  
\v 9 Bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Nde jombe.” Bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Nga jombe! Nambu atehi pe kulengana naku.” 
\p Jombi mweni akapwaghike, “Nepani nde jombi.” 
\p  
\v 10 Bhela bhakundalukile, “Bho, mihu ghaku ghayekuliwi bhole?” 
\p  
\v 11 Jombi akabhayangike, “Mundu jola joalowakeka Yesu akatendiki litopi, akambakiki mumihu, na kumbwaghila, ‘Ujenda ku litanda la Siloamu, ukachamba machi kumihu.’ Bhela nakapiti, na kuchamba, na nakapatiki kulola.” 
\p  
\v 12 Bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, abhi kwaku jonihojo?” 
\p Akayangike, “Nepani ngachemanye!” 
\s1 Mafalisayo bhapala kumanya kulama kwaka ngalola 
\p  
\v 13 Bhela bhakumpeliki kwa Mafalisayo mundu jola joakabhi ngalola pamwandi.  
\v 14 Bhela lichobha heli Yesu paakalenganaki litopi na kughayekula mihu ghaka mundu hoju, lakabhi Lichobha la Sabato.  
\v 15 Bhela Mafalisayo bhakundaluki kabhete mundu jola ntundu bholi moapati kulola. Akabhapwaghile, “Akanyeghi litopi panani ja mihu, na nepani nakachambiki machi, na sajenu nola.” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhela Mafalisayo bhakumu bhakapwaghike, “Mundu hoju ngacheakahumiki kwaka Chapanga, kwa ndandi ngacheakamula Lichobha la Sabato.” 
\p Bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Bho, aweza bholi mundu mwana mahoku kutenda nginyulila ngati yeniheye?” Kukabhi na kulekana pachilanda jabhu. 
\p  
\v 17 Bhela bhakundaluki mundu jola joakabhi ngalola mala ja kabheli, “Bho, wehapa upwagha bholi malobhi ghaki kubhokana na moakuyekuli mihu ghako?” 
\p Jombi akapwaghike, “Jombi nde mlota waka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 18 Bhela ihongozi bha Bhayahude ngachebhahobhali malobhi ghaki, gha kubha akabhi ngalola, na akapatiki kulola, mbaka pabhakabhalohiki bhabheleka bhaki mundu jola joakapatiki kulola.  
\v 19 Bhakabhalalukili bhabheleka bhaki, “Bho, hajoju le mwana winu, jompwagha kubha akabhelakiki ngalola? Bho, henu apatiki bholi kulola?” 
\p  
\v 20 Bhabheleka bhaki bhakayangike, “Tumanya kubha hajoju nde mwana witu, na kabheti akabhelakiki ngalola.  
\v 21 Nambu ntundu moalole sajenu ngachetumanyi, jombi nde akolike, mundalukya jombi, anaalilongalya mwene!”  
\v 22 Bhabheleka bhaki bhakalongi ghanihagha kwa ndandi bhakabhi bhabhajoghopa Bhayahude, maghambu Bhayahude bhakabhi bhajomwi kujetanganela kubha mundu anaanjetakili kubha Yesu nde Kristo, anaatopuliwa kunja ja nyumba ja kuhimanganila.  
\v 23 Nde ndandi bhabheleka bhaki bhakapwaghiki, “Hajoju akolike, mundalukya jombe!” 
\p  
\v 24 Bhela bhakundohiki kabhete mala ja kabheli mundu jola joakabhelakiki ngalola, na kumpwaghila, “Umpekya Chapanga ulumbalilu! Tepani tumanyi kubha mundu hajoju joakulamihe nde mwana mahoku.” 
\p  
\v 25 Bhela mundu jola akayangike, “Kubha jombi nde mwana mahoku au nga mwana mahoku, ngachemanya. Nambu chindu chimu chemanya, kubha nakabhi ngalola, na sajenu nola.” 
\p  
\v 26 Bhela bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, akuhengi kike? Bho, akuyekwi mihu kwa indela bhole?” 
\p  
\v 27 Akabhapwaghile, “Nyomwi kumpwaghila, wala ngachenjowine. Bho, mbona mpala kujowana kabhete? Bho, Mabhanganya nanamu mpala kubha bhabhulwa bhake?” 
\p  
\v 28 Bhela bhakuntondwili, bhakapwaghaje, “Wehapa nde wa mbulwa waka mundu jola, nambu tepani nde bhabhulwa bhaka Musa.  
\v 29 Tepani tumanyi kubha Chapanga akalongili na Musa, nambu mundu jonijola ngachetumanyi koahumike!” 
\p  
\v 30 Mundu jola akayangike, “Haleli nde lijambu la kukangacha! Kubha mwehapa ngachemmanya koahuma, najombi akaniyekwi mihu!  
\v 31 Tumanya kubha Chapanga ngacheajowanela bhana mahoku, nambu mundu joanjoghopa Chapanga, na kughahenga mapalu ghaka Chapanga, anjowanela jonihoju.  
\v 32 Kutumbula kubhombakeka kwa ndema ngachetujowini kubha mundu andamihi jokapi jola joabhelakiki ngalola.  
\v 33 Ngati mundu hajoju ngacheakahumiki kwa Chapanga, ngaakaweziki kuhenga lihengu lokapi lela.” 
\p  
\v 34 Bhombi bhakayangike, “Wehapa ukabhelakiki na kukolela mu mahoku pela, bho, nanau utubhola tepani?” Bhakumpihiki kunja ja nyumba ja kuhimangani Bhayahude. 
\s1 Ungalolola wa Roho 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu akajowini kubha bhumpihiki kunja ja nyumba ja kuhimangani Bhayahude, najombi paakumbweni akumpwaghile, “Bho, wehapa le unhobhalela Mwana waka Chapanga?” 
\p  
\v 36 Mundu hoju akayangike, “Jombi nde nane, Bambo, nahuli mbata kunhobhalela?” 
\p  
\v 37 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ujomwi kumbona, najombi nde joalongela na wehapa sajeno.” 
\p  
\v 38 Akapwaghike, “Bambo, nhobhalela.” Najombi akunjojabhile. 
\p  
\v 39 Yesu akapwaghike, “Nepani nhikiki pundema ghongone kubhatemula bhandu, nahuli bhala bhangakulola bhalolaje, na bhala bhabhalola bhabya akangalola.” 
\p  
\v 40 Mafalisayo bhakumu bhabhakabhi papamu naku bhakajowini ghanighala, bhakumpwaghile, “Bho, tepani natatu tubhi le akangalola?” 
\p  
\v 41 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ngati mwakabhi akangalola, ngamwakabhonakini kubha mbi na mahoku, nambu mwehapa mpwagha kubha ‘Tulola,’ bhela mbonikana kubha mbi na mahoku.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Ulenganesu waka mdima wambone 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Chakaka, numpwaghila, jola jwangakujingila pundyangu mu libheghi la mambeleli, nambu akwela kwa kupetela pandu pangi, jonihoju nde mwihe najombi nde mnyaghula.  
\v 2 Nambu joajingila pundyangu, jonihoju nde mdima wa mambelele.  
\v 3 Mlonda wa pundyangu anhoghulela jonihoju, na mambeleli ghajowana sauti jake, najombi aghaloha mambeleli kwa mahina ghabhu, na kughapeleka kunja.  
\v 4 Najombi paaghapiha kunja mambeleli ghaki ghokapi, aghalongulela, na mambeleli ghala ghunjengalela, maghambu bhajimanya sauti jake.  
\v 5 Mambeleli hagha ngaghawezi kunjengalela ngeni ng'o, nambu anaghuntilaje, maghambu ngachebhajimanyi sauti jaka ngeni.” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu akabhapwaghi ulenganesu aghoghu, nambu bhombi ngachebhamanyi mambu ghaakabhi abhapwaghila. 
\s1 Yesu Mdima wambone 
\p  
\v 7 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghi kabhete, “Chakaka, numpwaghila nepani nde ndyangu wa mambelele.  
\v 8 Bhokapi bhabhanongulile nde bhihe na bhanyaghula, nambu mambeleli ngacheghajowanile.  
\v 9 Nepani nde ndyangu. Mundu anaajingi kwangu nepani, anaakengalikaje, anaajingala na kupita, najombi anaapata malelelo.  
\v 10 Mwihi ahika pe kwa ndandi ja kujibha, kukoma, na kuyonanga. Nepani nakahikiki nahuli bhabya na womi, kabheti bhabya naku womi wamaheli.” 
\p  
\v 11 “Nepani nde mdima wambone. Mdima wambone aubhoha womi waki kwa ndandi ja mambelele.  
\v 12 Nambu mundu wa malepu, wala nga mdima wa mambelele, ambaju mambeleli nga ghake, paalibhona libweha lihika, aghaleka mambelele na mweni kutila. Na libweha lighakamula na kughapechangana.  
\v 13 Mundu hoju atila, wala ngacheaghajali mambelele, kwa ndandi abhi mundu wa malepu pela.  
\v 14 Nepani nde mdima wambone, na naghamanya mambelele ghangu, na mambelele ghangu ghamanye.  
\v 15 Ngati bhela Atati moamanyi nepani, na nepani monimmanyi Atati. Na nepani niubhoha womi wangu kwa ndandi ja mambelele.  
\v 16 Na mili kabheti na mambeleli ghangi, ghaghu nga gha libheghi lendeno, na ghanihagha naghombe imbalika kughaleta, na sauti jangu anabhajowanaje, na bhela anakukubhaje na lipogha limu na mdima jumu.” 
\p  
\v 17 “Atati wangu ambala nepani, maghambu nubhoha womi wangu, nahuli nupataje kabhete.  
\v 18 Nga mundu joamokela womi wangu, nambu nepani nubhoha namwete. Mili na lujiniku lwa kuubhoha, na mili na lujiniku lwa kuukelebhuha kabhete. Anana nde Atati wangu moanaghalakile nhengaje.” 
\p  
\v 19 Kukabhi kabheti na ughabhaniku wa Bhayahude, kwa ndandi ja malobhi ghanihagha.  
\v 20 Bhamaheli bhabhu bhakapwaghike, “Hajoju abhi na lijobhe, na kabheti mwanamangongo! Bho, maghambu kiki munjowanela?” 
\p  
\v 21 Bhangi bhakapwaghike, “Malobhi ghanihagha nga ghaka mundu joabhi na lijobhe. Bho, lijobhi liweza kaghayeku mihu ghaka ngalola?” 
\s1 Yesu akanakika na Bhayahude 
\p  
\v 22 Bhela ku Yelusalemu hoku kukabhili na Uwangalalu wa kubheka wakifu Nyumba jaka Chapanga, na chikahi hechi chakabhi chikahi cha imbepu.  
\v 23 Yesu akabhi akajendajenda mu Nyumba jaka Chapanga, mu liwangala laka Solomoni.  
\v 24 Bhela Bhayahude bhakamuyongalwiti, na kumpwaghila, “Bho, mbaka lile anautung'ahaje mitima jitu? Ngati wehapa nde wa Kristo, utupwaghila hotuhotu.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu akabhayangike, “Numpwaghile, nambu mwehapa ngachemuhobhalela. Mahengu ghangani ghanihenga kwa lihina la Atati wangu, nde ghaghanandila.  
\v 26 Nambu mwehapa ngachemuhobhalela, maghambu mwehapa ngachembili mu mambeleli ghangu.  
\v 27 Mambeleli ghangu ghajowana sauti jangu. Nanatu naghamanye, naghombi ghanyengalela.  
\v 28 Nanatu naghapekeha womi wa mileli, wala ngaghapoteli ng'o. Kabheti nga mundu joaweza kubhanyaghula kuhuma mu mabhoku ghangu.  
\v 29 Atati wangu, joambeki bhanihabha, nde nkolongwa kupeta bhokapi, kabheti nga mundu joaweza kubhanyaghula kuhuma mumabhoku gha Atati wangu.  
\v 30 Nepani na Atati wangu tubhi jumu.” 
\p  
\v 31 Bhela Bhayahude bhakatondwi maganga kabheti nahuli bhundapulaje.  
\v 32 Yesu akabhayangike, “Mahengu ghamboni ghamaheli nundangihe, ghaghahuma kwa Atati wangu, bho, kwa ndandi ja lihengu bhole pamahengu ghanihagha mpala kunapula kwa maganga?” 
\p  
\v 33 Bhayahude bhakamuyangike, “Ngechetukulapu maganga kwa ndandi ja mahengu ghambone, nambu kwa ndandi ja kutondola, na kwa ndandi wehapa weubhi wa mundu, ulitenda wamwete kubha nde Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu akabhayangike, “Bho, ngacheilembakiki mu Shelia hinu kubha, ‘Nepani nakapwaghiki, kubha mwehapa nde ichapanga?’  
\v 35 Ngati akabhalohiki ichapanga, bhala bhalakabhahiki Lilobhi laka Chapanga, naghombi Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha chakaka machobha ghokapi,  
\v 36 henu jola ambaju Atati akungolwili na kuntuma pundema, maghambu kiki mbwaghi kubha nuntondola Chapanga, pambwagha, ‘Nepani nde Mwana waka Chapanga?’  
\v 37 Ngati ngachenhenga mahengu gha Atati wangu, ngamwinhobhalela.  
\v 38 Nambu ananaghahenga, hata ngati ngachemunihobhalela nepani, mughahobhalyaje mahengu ghanihagha nahuli mpataje kumanya, na kuhobhalela, kubha Atati abhi mkati jangu, na nepani mili mkati ja Atati.” 
\p  
\v 39 Bhela bhakapaliki kabheti kunkamula, nambu Yesu akabhokiki mu mabhoku ghabhu. 
\p  
\v 40 Yesu akapiti kabhete kwihi ja nkoka Yoludani, pandu Yohana Mbatizaje paakabhi abatiza pakutumbula hapa, na kutama konihoku.  
\v 41 Bhandu bhamaheli bhakunjendi Yesu, na kupwagha, “Yohana ngacheakatendiki ngangachu jokapi jela, nambu mambu ghokapi Yohana ghaakalongili panani jaka mundu hajoju ghakabhi gha chakaka.”  
\v 42 Bhandu bhamaheli konihoku bhakunhobhali Yesu. 
\c 11  
\s1 Kupotela kwaka Lazalo 
\p  
\v 1 Bhela mundu jumu joakalowakiki Lazalo akabhi mtamwa. Jombi akabhi atama ku Besania, mwenehi wa chijiji cheatamika Malia na ndombu waki Masa.  
\v 2 Jonihoju akabhi nde Malia jola joakampakiki Bambo mahuta gha kunungila wichu, na kughahungula magholu ghaki kwa majunju ghaki. Lazalo mbeli waka Malia akabhi mtamwa.  
\v 3 Bhela bhalombu bhaki bhabheli bhala bhakatumiki ubholu kwaka Yesu, na kumpwaghila, “Bambo, nkochi waku joumpala jola atenda kulwala.” 
\p  
\v 4 Yesu paakajowini ghanihagha, akapwaghike, “Chitamu achechi nga cha kupotela, nambu kwa ndandi ja ulumbalilu waka Chapanga, nahuli Mwana waka Chapanga alumbalikaje mu chitamu chenihechi.” 
\p  
\v 5 Bhela Yesu akumpaliki Masa, Malia, na Lazalo.  
\v 6 Yesu paakajowini kubha Lazalo nde mtamwa, akajendali kutama pandu panipala kwa machobha ghabheli nakanopi.  
\v 7 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghi bhabhulwa bhaki, “Tujendaje kabhete ku Yudea!” 
\p  
\v 8 Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakumpwaghile, “Mbola, kwichu kwichu pela Bhayahude bhakapaliki kukulapula kwa maganga, bho, nanau upala kujenda kabheti konihoko?” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu akabhayangike, “Bho, Masaa gha muhi nga komi na ghabhele? Mundu anaajenda muhi ngachealikobhandola, maghambu aubhona unang'anu wa ndema ghone.  
\v 10 Nambu anaajendiki ikilu alikobhandola, maghambu unang'anu ngacheubhi mkati jake.”  
\v 11 Yesu paakajomwi kupwagha malobhi ghanihagha, akabhapwaghile, “Nkochi witu Lazalo aghonile, nambu nepani ananyenda kunjumuwa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakumpwaghile, “Bambo, anangati aghoni lughonu pela, anaalamaje.” 
\p  
\v 13 Yesu akabhi alongalela mambu gha kupotela kwaka Lazalo, nambu bhombi bhaholakya apwagha kubha Lazalo aghoni lughonu pela.  
\v 14 Bela Yesu akabhapwaghi hotuhotu, “Lazalo apotile.  
\v 15 Nambu kwa ndandi jinu nhekalela kwa kubha ngachenakabhi konihoko, nahuli mpata kuhobhalela, nambu sajenu tujendaje kwake.” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhela Tomaso, joalowakika Mapaha, akabhapwaghi bhabhulwa bhajaki, “Tujendaje na tepani, nahuli tukapotilaje papamu na Yesu!” 
\s1 Yesu nde uyohakeku na wome 
\p  
\v 17 Bhela Yesu paakahikiki konihoku, akunketani Lazalo kubha ajomwi kutaghakika mulitengeli kwa machobha ncheche.  
\v 18 Na chijiji cha Besania chakabhi pambipi na Yelusalemu, utali waki ukabhi ngati kilometa itatu.  
\v 19 Bhayahude bhamaheli bhakabhi bhahikike kwaka Masa na Malia, nahuli kubhajeghe mtima kwa ndandi jaka mbeli wabhu. 
\p  
\v 20 Bhela Masa paakajowini kubha Yesu atenda kuhika, akapiti kunjopalela, nambu Malia akahighali atami kunyumba.  
\v 21 Masa akumpwaghi Yesu, “Bambo, ngati wehapa ukabhi pambane, mbeli wangu ngaakapotile.  
\v 22 Nambu hata sajenu manyi kubha, chokapi chewandobhaje Chapanga, Chapanga anaakupekyaje.” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mbeli waku anahyokaje kabhete.” 
\p  
\v 24 Masa akumpwaghile, “Manyi kubha anaayokaje pa uyohakeku wa bhakuwa mu lichobha la kujomukela.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Nepani nde uyohakeku hoghu, na nde nenabhapekeha bhandu womi. Mundu jokapi joanhobhale nepani, hata ngati anaapotile, anaakubha atama,  
\v 26 na kila mundu joatama na kunhobhalela nepani ngaapoteli mileli. Bho, uhobhalela ghanihagha?” 
\p  
\v 27 Masa akumpwaghile, “Ena, Bambo, nepani nhobhalela kubha wehapa nde wa Kristo, Mwana waka Chapanga, jola joahika pani pundema.” 
\s1 Yesu alela mahole 
\p  
\v 28 Yesu paakajomwi kulongela ghanihagha, Masa akapiti kundoha Malia ndombu waki pandu pa kanjika, na kumpwaghila, “Mbola ahikike, na akulowa.”  
\v 29 Malia paakajowini, akajemiki manyata, na kujenda mbaka paakabhi Yesu.  
\v 30 Yesu akabhi ngacheahikiki mkati ja chijiji, nambu akabhi akali pandu pala Masa paakunjopalile.  
\v 31 Bhela Bhayahude bhabhabhi panyumba pala na Malia, bhakunjeghala mtima, pabhakumbweni Malia ntundu moakajemi manyata na kubhoka, bhakunjengalile. Koni bhakaholakya kubha ajenda kumatengeli nahuli alela konihoku. 
\p  
\v 32 Bhela Malia paakahikiki pandu pala paakabhi Yesu, na kumbona, akachikimi pamagholu ghaka Yesu, na kumpwaghila, “Bambo, ngati ukabhi pambane, mbeli wangu ngaakapotile!” 
\p  
\v 33 Yesu paakumbweni Malia alela, na Bhayahude bhaakalongini naku bhala nabhombi bhalela, Yesu ukambiniki mtima waki, na kung'ahakika muntima waki,  
\v 34 akapwaghike, “Bho, mumbekiki kwako?” 
\p Bhakumpwaghile, “Bambo, uhika ulingaje.” 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu akaleliki mahole.  
\v 36 Bhela Bhayahude bhakapwaghike, “Ndingalyaje ntundu moakumpali Lazalo!” 
\p  
\v 37 Nambu bhangi bhabhu bhakapwaghike, “Bho, hajoju joakamuyekwi mihu ngalola, ngacheakaweziki kuntenda na Lazalo ngayipotela?” 
\s1 Yesu amuhyoha Lazalo 
\p  
\v 38 Bhela Yesu akabya kabhete umbina mtima waki, akahikiki palitengeli. Litengeli heli lakabhi likolo, na liganga lakabhi libhekakiki panani jaki.  
\v 39 Yesu akapwaghike, “Mulibhoha liganga!” 
\p Masa ndombu waka jola joapotile, akumpwaghile, “Bambo, kwa sajenu atumbwi kununga, kwa ndandi abhi ntuhi kwa machobha ncheche!” 
\p  
\v 40 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Bho, nepani ngachenukupwaghile kubha ngati anauhobhalela, anaubhona ulumbalilu waka Chapanga?”  
\v 41 Bhela bhakalibhohiki liganga lela. Na Yesu akalingalili kunani kumahunde, na kupwagha, “Atati, nukuchengula kwa ndandi unyowine.  
\v 42 Nanatu nakamanyi kubha wehapa unyowana machobha ghokapi, nambu kwa ndandi ja bhandu bhabhajemiki pambani nakapwaghiki ghanihagha, nahuli bhandu bhabhabhi pambane, bhapata kuhobhalela kubha wehapa nde weundumike.”  
\v 43 Najombi paakajomwili kulongela ghanihagha, Yesu akaleliki kwa sauti ngolongwa, “Lazalo, uhikaje koni kunja!”  
\v 44 Na jola joakapotile akapitiki kunja, koni akabya akongakiki sanda mumagholu na mumabhoku, na pamihu jaki. Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Mumbopulaje, na mundekaje ajendaje.” 
\s1 Njama ja kunkoma Yesu 
\r Matayo 26:1-5; Mako 14:1-2; Luka 22:1-2 
\p  
\v 45 Bhela Bhayahude bhamaheli bhabhakabhi bhahikiki kwaka Malia, na kughabhona mambu ghala ghaakahengiki Yesu, bhakunhobhalile.  
\v 46 Nambu bhakumu bhabhu bhakapiti kwa Mafalisayo, na kubhapwaghila mambu ghokapi ghaakahengiki Yesu.  
\v 47 Bhela ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku papamu na Mafalisayo bhakahengiki uhimanganu wa Pachengu Pakolongwa pa Bhayahude, na kupwagha, “Bho, tuhenga kike? Maghambu mundu hajoju ahenga nginyulila yamaheli nakanopi!\fig Mpenganyambiku wa Kiyahude|alt="A Jewish Priest" src="18 Priest.jpg" size="col" ref="11:47" \fig* 
\v 48 Ngati anatundekiki ajendalya kuhenga bhenibhela, bhandu bhokapi anabhunhobhalyaje, na bhakolongwa bha Bhaloma anabhahikaje na kutubhokela pandu pitu na litaifa litu.” 
\p  
\v 49 Mundu jumu pachilanda jabhu, joalowakika Kayafa, joakabhi Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa chaka chela, akabhapwaghile, “Mabhanganya ngachemulimanyi lilobhi lokapi lela!  
\v 50 Bho, ngachemuholalela kubha nde mbanga mundu jumu kupotela kwa ndandi ja bhandu bhokapi, kuliku bhandu bhokapi bha litaifa litu kuyonangeka?”  
\v 51 Ngacheakalongili ghanihagha kwa maholalelu ghaki mweni, nambu kwa ndandi akabhi Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa chaka chela, akalotiki kubha Yesu anaapotilaje kwa ndandi ja litaifa la Bhayahude.  
\v 52 Wala nga kwa ndandi ja Bhayahude pela, nambu papamu na hagha abhabhonganaje bhana bhaka Chapanga bhabhapechangine, nahuli bhabya bhamu. 
\p  
\v 53 Bhela kutumbula lichobha lela ihongozi bha Bhayahude bhakajongini kunkoma Yesu.  
\v 54 Bhela Yesu ngacheakajendiki kabhete kwa palanga pachilanda ja Bhayahude, nambu akabhokiki konihoku, na kujenda pandu pambipi na lipololu, mbaka ku muchi ghoulowakeka Efulaimu, na kutama konihoku papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki. 
\p  
\v 55 Chikahi cha Uwangalalu wa Pasaka ja Bhayahude jakabhi jiheghalile, na bhandu bhamaheli bhakabhi bhakwela kuhuma kumighonda na kujenda ku Yelusalemu, nahuli kuligholola kwa ndandi ja kunjojabhela Chapanga mangani ja kuhika Pasaka.  
\v 56 Bhela bhakabhi bhundonda Yesu, bhakalaluhini koni bhakabya bhajemanile mu liwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, “Bho, mbona bhole? Bho, ibhonikana kubha ngaahiki ng'o pauhangalalu ghone?”  
\v 57 Bhapenganyambiku bhakolongwa papanu na Mafalisayo bhakabhi bhabhohiki amuli ja kubha anangati mundu amanyi paabhi Yesu, aleta ubholu, nahuli bhapata kunkamula. 
\c 12  
\s1 Yesu bhumpaka mahuta ghaghanungila wichu 
\r Matayo 26:6-13; Mako 14:3-9 
\p  
\v 1 Machobha sita mangani ja Uwangalalu wa Pasaka, Yesu akapiti ku Besania, koatamika Lazalo ambaju Yesu akamuhyohiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa.  
\v 2 Konihoku bhakumbeki chilebhi cha chimihi, najombi Masa akabhi abhatumakila. Lazalo akabhi jumu wa bhala bhabhakabhi bhakula papamu na Yesu.  
\v 3 Bhela Malia akatoliki nusu lita ja mahuta ghaghanungila wichu ghaghalenganakiki kwa nkongu wa nalido ja mbiya yamaheli, na kumpaka mumagholu ghaka Yesu na kunhungula kwa majunju ghaki. Nyumba jokapi jakatweli unungilu wa mahuta ghanihagha.  
\v 4 Henu Yuda Isikalioti, jumu wa bhabhulwa komi na bhabheli, jonihoju nde joanaang'anambuka Yesu, akapwaghike,  
\v 5 “Bho, maghambu kiki manungilu ghanihagha ngacheghakahemaliwi kwa ipandi mia tatu yeilenganakiki kwa madini gha feza, na mbija yene kubhapekeha bhahocho?”  
\v 6 Yuda akapwaghiki bhenibhela, nga kwa ndandi ja kubhabhonela chiha bhahocho, nambu kwa ndandi akabhi mwihi. Maghambu jombi nde joakabhi abheka mfuku wa mbija, najombi akabhi ajibha yela yeyabhekakiki monihomu. 
\p  
\v 7 Nambu Yesu akapwaghike, “Ngamung'aha mabhu hoju! Mundekaje aghabhekaje kwa ndandi ja lichobha la kutaghakika kwangu.  
\v 8 Kwa ndandi bhahocho mbinabhu machobha ghokapi, nambu ngankubhi na nepani machobha ghokapi.” 
\s1 Njama ja kunkoma Lazalo 
\p  
\v 9 Bhayahude bhamaheli bhakajowini kubha Yesu akabhi ku Besania. Henu, bhakahikiki konihoku nga kwa ndandi ja kumbona Yesu pela, nambu bhumbona kabheti na Lazalo, ambaju Yesu akamuhyohiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa.  
\v 10 Nambu ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku bhakatendiki njama ja kunkoma kabhete Lazalo,  
\v 11 maghambu kwa ndandi jaki Bhayahude bhamaheli bhakabhakaniki ihongozi bhabhu, na kunhobhale Yesu. 
\s1 Yesu ajingi ku Yelusalemu kwa chiheku 
\r Matayo 21:1-11; Mako 11:1-11; Luka 19:28-40 
\p  
\v 12 Chilabhu jaki lipogha la bhandu bhabhakahikiki kwa ndandi ja Uwangalalu wa Pasaka, bhakajowini kubha Yesu abhi mwindela kuhika ku Yelusalemu.  
\v 13 Bhela bhakatoliki mambandi gha mikongu ja mitende, na kujenda kumpengana, na kujamalila bhakapwaghaje, “Chapanga apengalikaje! Apengalika jonihoju joahika kwa lihina laka Bambo! Apengalikaje Nkolongwa wa Izilaeli!” 
\p  
\v 14 Yesu akapatiki mwanaliponda jumu, na kukwela na kutama panani jaki, ngati moghalembakike mu Malembelu Mahuhu, 
\q1  
\v 15 “Ngamwijoghopa bhandu bha muchi wa Sayuni! 
\q1 Lingalyaje, Nkolongwa waku ahika, 
\q1 akweliki mwanaliponda.” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhabhulwa bhaka Yesu ngachebhakamanyi mambu ghanihagha hoti, nambu Yesu paakahyokike kuhuma kwa bhakuwa na paakalumbaliki, panihapa nde bhabhulwa bhaki bhakakombwiki kubha mambu ghanihagha ghakabhi ghalembakiki kwa ndandi jaki, na kubha bhakuntendi jombi. 
\p  
\v 17 Lipogha la bhandu bhala bhabhakabhi papamu na Yesu chikahi paandohika Lazalo kuhuma mulitengeli, na kumuhyoha kuhuma kwa bhakuwa, bhakabhalandi bhandu mambu ghala ghaghapitalile.  
\v 18 Kwa ndandi jeniheji lipogha la bhandu lakapiti kumpengana, maghambu bhakajowini kubha Yesu akahengiki ngangachu jeniheji.  
\v 19 Bhela Mafalisayo pabhakaghaweni ghanihagha bhakapwaghanile, “Mbona? Bho, ngatuwezi kutenda chokapi? Lingalyaje, bhandu bhokapi pundema bhunjengale jombi.” 
\s1 Bhagiliki bhakumu bhapala kumbona Yesu 
\p  
\v 20 Kukabhi na Bhagiliki bhakumu pachilanda ja bhala bhabhahikiki ku Yelusalemu kujojabhela chikahi cha Uwangalalu wa Pasaka.  
\v 21 Bhanihabha bhakunjendi Filipo, mwenehi wa ku Betisaida ja inchi ja ku Galilaya, na kundobha, bhakapwaghaje, “Nkolongwa, tepani tupala kumbona Yesu.” 
\p  
\v 22 Filipo akapiti kumpwaghi Andulea, kabheti Andulea na Filipo bhakumpwaghi Yesu.  
\v 23 Yesu akabhayangike, “Lisaa la kulumbalika kwaka Mwana waka Mundu lihikike!  
\v 24 Numpwaghi chakaka, imbeju ya ingano nangakuhabhuka paluhombi na kuwa, ihighalila ngati imbeju kanjika jaki. Nambu ngati anaihawiki pahi na kuwa, jibheleka imbeju yamaheli.  
\v 25 Mundu jokapi joaghapala matamu ghaki anaaghahobhihaje, na mundu jokapi joaghahobheha matamu ghaki mu ndema ghoni anaaghakengalyaje hata womi wa mileli.  
\v 26 Mundu jokapi joapala kundumakila, impalika anyengalyaje, na nepani pamili, panihapa nde na mtumika wangu payibyaje. Kabheti mundu jokapi joandumakila nepani, Atati wangu anaampekya utopelu. 
\s1 Yesu alongela panani ja kupotela kwaki 
\p  
\v 27 “Sajenu roho jangu jing'ahika, bho, henu mbwagha kike? ‘Atati, ungengalyaje mu chikahi chenu!’ Nambu nde kwa ndandi ja ghanihagha nakahikiki nahuli naghapetilaje mang'ahiku gha chikahi chenu.  
\v 28 Atati ulilumbalyaje lihina laku!” 
\p Panihapa sauti kuhuma kunani kumahunde jakapwaghike, “Nililumbalile, na ananililumbalya kabhete.” 
\p  
\v 29 Lipogha la bhandu bhabhakabhi pandu pala bhakajowini sauti jela, na bhakumu bhabhu bhakapwaghike, “Jeniheji nde sauti ja kulundamila kwa chitobhi.” Nambu bhangi bhakapwaghiki, “Mtumika wa kunani kwaka Chapanga atehi kulongela naku!” 
\p  
\v 30 Nambu Yesu akabhayangiki, “Sauti jeniheji ngachejabhili kwa ndandi jangu nepani, nambu kwa ndandi jinu mwehapa.  
\v 31 Sajenu nde chikahi cha kutemuliwa kwa ndema ghoni, henu Shetani, nkolongwa wa ndema ghoni anaalekalikaje kunja.  
\v 32 Nambu nepani panikwehakikaje kunani kuhuma pundema, ananabhahutaje bhandu bhokapi bhahikaje kwangu.”  
\v 33 Yesu akapwaghiki ghanihagha akalangiya kubha anapotilaje kwa ntundu bhole. 
\p  
\v 34 Bhela lipogha la bhandu lela lakalapwili njobhela lakapwaghaje, “Tujowini mu Shelia jitu kubha Kristo anatama mileli. Bho, uweza bholi henu kupwagha kubha impalika Mwana waka Mundu kujinuliwa kunani? Bho, henu Mwana waka Mundu nde nane?” 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu akapwaghike, “Unang'anu wakona ubhi na mwehapa kwa chikahi kichokope. Njendaje koni mbili na unang'anu, nahuli lwihi ngalwampata, maghambu joajenda mulwihi ngacheamanya koajenda.  
\v 36 Bhela kwa ndandi mbili na unang'anu, muuhobhalyaje unang'anu hoghu, nahuli mpata kubha mabhana bha unang'anu.” 
\s1 Bhandu ngachebhabhi na uhobhalelu 
\p Paakajomwi kulonge ghanihagha, Yesu akabhokike, na kulihiya nahuli ngabhumbona.  
\v 37 Nambu Yesu papamu na kutenda ngangachu hayeyi yokapi palongi jabhu, bhombi ngachebhunhobhalile.  
\v 38 Nahuli ghapata kupitalila malobhi ghaakapwaghiki mlota Isaya, 
\q1 “Bambo, bho, nde nane joakauhobhalile ubholu wito? 
\q1 Na bho, nde nane joayekuliwi makili ghaka Bambo?” 
\p  
\v 39 Ndemana bhombi ngachebhahobhalile, kwa ndandi Isaya akapwaghiki kabhete, 
\q1  
\v 40 “Chapanga abhatendiki akangalola, 
\q1 ajitendiki kunonopa mitima jabhu, 
\q1 ngabhilola kwa mihu ghabhu, 
\q1 ngabhimanya kwa mitima jabhu, 
\q1 wala ngabhing'anambuka, 
\q1 nahuli mbata kubhalamiha, apwagha Bambo.” 
\p  
\v 41 Mlota Isaya akapwaghiki malobhi ghanihagha kwa ndandi akauweni ulumbalilu waka Yesu, na akapwaghiki malobhi ghaki. 
\p  
\v 42 Hata bhela, bhamaheli pachilanda ja ihongozi bha Bhayahude bhakunhobhali Yesu. Nambu kwa ndandi ja Mafalisayo, ngachebhakapwaghiki palanga, kwa kujoghopa kubhatopola mu nyumba ya kuhimangani Bhayahude.  
\v 43 Kwa ndandi bhombi bhakapaliki ulumbalilu wa bhandu kuliku ulumbalilu waka Chapanga. 
\s1 Malobhi ghaka Yesu anaghatemula bhandu 
\p  
\v 44 Yesu akajamalila kwa sauti ngolongwa, akapwaghaje, “Mundu joanhobhalela nepani, ngacheanhobhale nepani pela, nambu bhelabhela anhobhalela jola joandumike.  
\v 45 Na jola joaningali nepani andingali jola joandumike.  
\v 46 Nepani nhikiki nahuli mya unang'anu wa pundema, nahuli kila mundu joanhobhale nepani ngayitama mulwihi.  
\v 47 Na ngati mundu anaaghajowini malobhi ghangu, nambu ngacheaghakamula, nepani ngachenuntemula. Maghambu ngachenhikiki kuutemula ndema, nambu kuukengalela ndema.  
\v 48 Mundu joangana nepani, jwangakughahobhalela malobhi ghangu, abhi na wa kuntemula. Lilobhi heli lenilipwaghiki nde lelantemulaje mu lichobha la kujomukela.  
\v 49 Maghambu nepani ngachenapwaghiki kwa ndandi ja lujiniku lwangu, nambu Atati joandumiki, nde joanaghalakili cha kupwagha na ntundu monipwaghilaje.  
\v 50 Nanatu manyi kubha amuli yaki ileta womi wa mileli. Bhela nepani nongela malobhi ghala pela ghaanaghalakili Atati.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Yesu abhagholola magholu bhabhulwa bhaki 
\p  
\v 1 Bhela, mangani ja lichobha la Uwangalalu wa Pasaka. Yesu akamanyi kubha chikahi chaki cha kubhoka pundema na kujenda kwa Atati waki chakabhi chihikike, akabhi abhapaliki bhandu bhaki bhabhabhi pundema, akabhapaliki mbaka pakujomukela. 
\p  
\v 2 Henu Yesu na bhabhulwa bhaki bhakabhi bhatemi kula chilebhi cha chimihi. Shetani akajomwi kunjeghela Yuda, mwana waka Simoni Isikalioti, maholalelu gha kung'anambuka Yesu.  
\v 3 Yesu akamanyi kubha Atati abhekiki hindu yokapi mu makili ghaki, na kubha jombi akahumiki kwaka Chapanga, na akelabhuka kwaka Chapanga,  
\v 4 akabhokiki pachilebhi, na kubhoha ingobhu jaki ja kunja na kubheka punkeghi, akatoliki chitambala, na kulikonga muchibhunu.  
\v 5 Panihapa akajeghi machi mu likalahi, na kutumbu kubhagholola bhabhulwa bhaki magholu, na kughahungula kwa chitambala chela cheakakongiki muchihunu.  
\v 6 Paakahikiki kwaka Simoni Petulu, Petulu akapwaghike, “Bambo, bho, wehapa anaung'olula nepani magholu?” 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu akamuyangiki, “Chendenda sajenu ngauchimanye, nambu anauchimanya palonge.” 
\p  
\v 8 Petulu akumpwaghile, “Wehapa ngaung'ololi nepani magholu ng'o!” 
\p Yesu akamuyangike, “Ngati nganukughololi magholu, wehapa ngaukubhi wa mbulwa wangu.” 
\p  
\v 9 Simoni Petulu akamuyangike, “Bambo, ung'olulaje, nga magholu pela, nambu papamu na mabhoku ghangu na mmutu wangu bhelabhela!” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mundu joajomwi kujogha hyegha jokapi apalika kugholola magholu pela, maghambu ajomwi kunyamba hyegha jokapi. Mwehapa mnyambike, nambu nga mabhokape.”  
\v 11 Yesu akamanyi jola joanaang'anambukaje, nde ndandi akapwaghiki, “Mwehapa mnyambike, nambu nga mabhokape.” 
\p  
\v 12 Yesu paakajomwi kubhagholola magholu bhabhulwa bhaki, akawatiki kabhete ingobhu jaki ja kunja na kukelabhuka na kutama kabhete, na kubhalalukila, “Bho, mmanyi ghanuntendile?”  
\v 13 “Mwehapa mnoha Mbola na Bambo, nanamu mpwagha wichu, maghambu nde momelile.  
\v 14 Henu anakubhi nepani, nemi Bambo winu na Mbola winu, nungolwili mwehapa magholu, impalika na mwehapa kugholulana magholu mabheti kwa mabheti.  
\v 15 Kwa ndandi nepani numpeki ulenganesu, nahuli na mwehapa mtendaje ngati nepani monuntendile.  
\v 16 Numpwaghi Chakaka, mtumika nga nkolongwa kumpeta bambo waki, wala mtumi nga nkolongwa kumpeta jola joantumike.  
\v 17 Anamughamanyi mambu ghanihagha, mbanga kwinu mwehapa ngati anamughatendike. 
\p  
\v 18 “Ngachembwagha kwinu mwehapa mabhokapi. Nepani nabhamanyi bhala bhanabhahawile. Nambu nahuli ghapitalyaje Malembu Mahuhu ghaghapwagha, ‘Jola joakuliki chilebhi changu, atehi kuning'anambuka.’  
\v 19 Nepani numpwaghili mambu ghanihagha sajenu mangani ngacheghapitalile, nahuli paghipitalyaje, mpata kuhobhalela kubha ‘Nepani nde Jombi.’  
\v 20 Numpwaghi Chakaka, mundu jokapi joanjopalela mundu jola jonumtumiki, anyopalela nepane. Na mundu jokapi joanyopalela nepane, anjopalela jombi joandumiki nepane.” 
\s1 Yesu alota ntundu mobhung'anambukyaje 
\r Matayo 26:20-25; Mako 14:17-21; Luka 22:21-23 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu paakajomwili kupwagha ghanihagha, akang'ahakiki mu roho jaki, akalandili hotuhotu, “Chakaka numpwaghila, jumu winu anaang'anambukaje.” 
\p  
\v 22 Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakalingalanili bheni kwa bheni, koni ngachebhamanyi kubha nde nane joandongalela.  
\v 23 Jumu wa bhabhulwa bhaki, ambaju Yesu akabhi ampala nakanopi, akabhi ajeghamakili pachihimba chaka Yesu.  
\v 24 Bhela Simoni Petulu akumpongi mbulwa jola chiwoku chaki, na kumpwaghila, “Undalukyaje, bho, ampwagha nane?” 
\p  
\v 25 Mbulwa hoju koni akabya ajeghamaki pachihimba chaka Yesu, akundalukile, “Bambo, bho, nde nane?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu akayangike, “Nde mundu jola jonampekyaje chipandi cha libumunda. Akatobhalili libumunda heli mumbale, na kumpekeha Yuda, mwana waka Simoni Isikalioti.”  
\v 27 Yuda paakajomwi kujopa chipandi cha libumunda heli, Shetani akunjingile. Bhela Yesu akumpwaghile, “Cheupala kuchihenga, uchihenga manyata!”  
\v 28 Wala nga mundu hata jumu wa bhala bhabhakabhi bhatemi pachilebhi joakamanyi ndandi kiki Yesu akumpwaghi bhenibhela.  
\v 29 Kwa kubha Yuda akabhi mbeka mbija, bhangi bhakaholali kubha Yesu akabhi ampwaghi akahemalaje hindu yeipalika kwa ndandi ja Uwangalalu wa Pasaka, au abhapekya bhahocho chokapi. 
\p  
\v 30 Yuda paakajomwi kujopa chipandi cha libumunda chela, palapala akapitiki kunja. Chikahi hechi kukabhi ikilu. 
\s1 Amuli Jahenu 
\p  
\v 31 Bhela Yuda paakajomwi kupita kunja, Yesu akapwaghike, “Sajenu Mwana waka Mundu alumbalike, najombi Chapanga alumbaliki mkati jaki.  
\v 32 Ngati Chapanga alumbaliki mkati jaka Mwana, Chapanga anaandumbalyaje Mwana mkati jaki mweni bhelabhela, najombi ngaakabhakile kundumbalila henu kateki.  
\v 33 Bhana bhango, chakona chikahi kichokopi mili na mwehapa. Anamunondaje nepani, na ngati monakabhapwaghile ihongozi bha Bhayahude kubha, ‘Nepani konyenda mwehapa ngamuwezi kuhika, bhelabhela sajenu numpwaghi mwehapa.’  
\v 34 Amuli jahenu numpekeha: Mpalanaje. Mpalanaje ngati nepani monumpali mwehapa.  
\v 35 Ngati anampalana mabheti kwa mabheti, bhandu bhokapi anabhamanyaje kubha mwehapa nde bhabhulwa bhangu.” 
\s1 Yesu alota kubha Petulu anaankanaje 
\r Matayo 26:31-35; Mako 14:27-31; Luka 22:31-34 
\p  
\v 36 Simoni Petulu akundalukile, “Bambo, bho, ujenda kwako?” 
\p Yesu akamuyangike, “Konyenda ngauwezi kunyengale sajenu, nambu anaunyengalyaje palongi.” 
\p  
\v 37 Petulu akundalukili kabhete, “Bambo, bho, maghambu kiki nepani nganiweza kukujengale sajenu? Nepani mi tayali kuubhoha womi wangu kwa ndandi jaku!” 
\p  
\v 38 Yesu akayangike, “Bho, chakaka le kubha wehapa anaubhoha womi waku kwa ndandi jangu? Chakaka nukupwaghila, mangani ja likongobhi ngachelibhekiki anaunganaje mala patatu.” 
\c 14  
\s1 Yesu nde indela ja kujenda kwa Atati 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ngamwikubha na choghohi mumitima jinu, munhobhale Chapanga, mnihobhalya na nepani bhelabhela.  
\v 2 Munyumba ja Atati wangu kubhi na matamu ghamaheli, ikabhi ngabhela, nakabya numpwaghile. Ndandi nyenda kunhandalila matamu.  
\v 3 Ngati anambiti na kunhandalila matamu, ananhika kabhete, na kuntola mwehapa kwangu, nahuli pandu pamili nepani, na mwehapa mbyaje.  
\v 4 Konyenda mukumanye, na indela mujimanye.” 
\p  
\v 5 Tomaso akundalukile, “Bambo, tepani ngachetumanyi koujenda, bho, anatuweza bhole kujimanya indela?” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu akayangike, “Nepani nde indela, chakaka na womi. Mundu ngacheaweza kuhika kwa Atati, nambu kwa kupetela kwangu nepani.  
\v 7 Ngati mkabhili mmanyi nepani, mkabya mummanyi na Atati wangu. Kutumbula sajenu mummanye, na kabhete mumbwene.” 
\p  
\v 8 Filipo akumpwaghile, “Bambo, utulangihaje Atati, chenihechi nde chetukipala.” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu akayangike, “Filipo, ndemi na mwehapa kwa machobha ghamaheli, bho, nanau ngacheunimanye? Mundu jokapi joamweni nepani, ambweni Atati. Bho, henu wehapa uweza bhole kupwagha, ‘Utulangihaje Atati?’  
\v 10 Bho, ngacheuhobhalela kubha nepani mi mkati ja Atati, na Atati abhi mkati jangu nepane? Malobhi ghanumpwaghila ngachembwagha kwa ndandi jangu namwete, nambu Atati joatama mkati jangu, aghatenda mahengu ghake.  
\v 11 Mnihobhalyaje pambwagha kubha nepani mi mkati ja Atati, na Atati abhi mkati jangu nepani! Nangabhela muhobhalyaje kwa ndandi ja mahengu ghala ghanaghatenda.  
\v 12 Numpwaghila Chakaka, jokapi joanhobhalela nepani, mahengu ghanaghahenga nepani, najombi anaaghahengaje. Ena, na mahengu makolongwa nakanopi kupeta ghanihagha anahengaje, kwa ndandi nepani nyenda kwa Atati.  
\v 13 Chokapi chemwilobhaje kwa lihina langu, anandendaje, nahuli Atati alumbalikaje mkati jaka Mwana.  
\v 14 Anandobhiki chindu chokapi kupetela lihina langu, anandendaje. 
\s1 Chilanga chaka Roho Mhuhu 
\p  
\v 15 “Ngati anambala nepani, anankamulaje amuli yangu.  
\v 16 Nanatu ananundobhaje Atati, najombi anaampekyaje Mjangatila najongi, nahuli atamaje na mwehapa mileli.  
\v 17 Jombi nde Roho wa chakaka. Ambaju bhandu bha pundema ngabhawezi kunjopalela, kwa ndandi ngachebhumbona, wala ngachebhummanye. Nambu mwehapa anamummanyaje, kwa ndandi atama kwinu, najombi anaakubhaje mkati jinu. 
\p  
\v 18 “Nganundeki mwehapa ngati bhakebha, ananhika kabheti kwinu.  
\v 19 Chakona chikahi kichokopi, bhandu bha pundema ngabhimoni kabhete, nambu mwehapa anammonaje. Kwa ndandi nepani mi mwomi, na mwehapa anamkubha bhomi.  
\v 20 Lichobha lela palihikaje, mwehapa anammanyaje kubha nepani mi mkati ja Atati wangu, na mwehapa mkati jangu, na nepani mkati jinu. 
\p  
\v 21 “Mundu jola joabhi na amuli yangu na kuikamula, jonihoju nde joambala nepani. Najombi joambala nepani, anaapalakikaje na Atati wangu, na nepani ananumpalaje, na kulilangiha kwaki.” 
\p  
\v 22 Panihapa Yuda, nga jola Yuda Isikalioti, akumpwaghile, “Bambo, bho, kubhi bhole wehapa upala kulilangiha kwitu, na wala nga kwa bhandu bha pundema?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu akayangike, “Mundu jokapi joambala nepani, anaakamulaje malobhi ghangu, na Atati wangu anaampalaje, nepani na Atati wangu anatuhikaje kwaki, na kuhenga matamu kwaki.  
\v 24 Mundu jokapi jwangakumbala nepani, ngacheaghakamula malobhi ghangu. Na malobhi ghamughajowana nga ghangu, nambu ghahumiki kwa Atati joandumike.” 
\p  
\v 25 “Mambu ghanihagha nde ghanakumpwaghile, chikahi panakabhi ndama papamu na mwehapa.  
\v 26 Mjangatila hoju, nde Roho Mhuhu, ambaju Atati anaantumaje kupetela lihina langu, anaambolaje mambu ghokapi, na kunkombosha mambu ghokapi ghanumpwaghile.” 
\p  
\v 27 “Lukwale nundekela, lukwale lwangu numpekeha. Monumpeke nepani, nga ngati bhandu bha pundema mobhumpekeha. Ngamwing'ahika mumitima jinu, wala ngamwijoghopa.  
\v 28 Mkajowini kubha nepani nakumpwaghile, ‘Nyenda, na ananhika kabheti kwinu.’ Ngati mkabhi mbala, mkabya muhekalile, kwa ndandi nyenda kwa Atati, maghambu Atati nde nkolongwa kupeta nepani.  
\v 29 Numpwaghi mambu ghanihagha sajenu mangani ngacheghapitalile, nahuli paghipitalyaje mpata kuhobhalela.  
\v 30 Nepani nganongeli na mwehapa malobhi ghamaheli kabhete, maghambu Shetani, nkolongwa wa ndema ghoni ahika, nambu jonihoju ngacheabhi na chindu kwangu,  
\v 31 nambu bhandu bha pundema bhapata kumanya kubha numpala Atati. Ngati bhela Atati moanaghalakile, bhenibhela nde monhengela.” 
\p Haya njemanyaje, na tujendaje. 
\c 15  
\s1 Yesu nde mzabibu wa chakaka 
\p  
\v 1 “Nepani nde mzabibu wa chakaka, na Atati wangu nde ndeme.  
\v 2 Kila limbandi mkati jangu langakupambika mapambiku, Atati wangu aliheketa. Na kila limbandi lelipambika mapambiku, Atati wangu alikulaghalila, nahuli lipambikaje mapambiku nakanopi.  
\v 3 Sajenu mwehapa njomwi kubha mwanyahi kwa ndandi ja malobhi ghala ghanakumpwaghile.  
\v 4 Mtamaje mkati jangu, na nepani mkati jinu. Ngati bhela limbandi molilepalela kupambika mapambiku kanjika jaki, nangakutama mkati ja mzabibu, bhelabhela na mwehapa ngamuwezi kupambika mapambiku, nangakutama mkati jangu.” 
\p  
\v 5 “Nepani nde mzabibu, na mwehapa nde mambandi. Joatama mkati jangu, na nepani mkati jaki, jonihoju apambika mapambiku nakanopi. Maghambu panga kubha nepani, mwehapa ngamuwezi kutenda chindu chokapi.  
\v 6 Mundu jokapi jwangakutama mkati jangu, anaalekalikaje kunja ngati limbandi na kunyala. Na bhandu anabhabhonganaje, na kughalekela pamoto, na kutinyika.  
\v 7 Ngati mwehapa anantami mkati jangu, na malobhi ghangu anaghatemi mkati jinu, ndobhaje chokapi chemchipala nanamu anampataje.  
\v 8 Bhela alumbalikaje Atati wangu, kwa bhela mompambaki mapambiku nakanopi, na kwa indela jeniheji anambya bhabhulwa bhangu.  
\v 9 Ngati Atati moambali nepani, nanatu monumpali mwehapa. Njendalyaje kutama mu upalu wangu.  
\v 10 Ngati anamkamwili amuli yangu, anamtamaje mu upalu wangu, ngati bhela nepani monikamulile amuli ya Atati wangu, na kutama mu upalu waki. 
\p  
\v 11 “Numpwaghili mambu ghanihagha, nahuli chiheku changu chibya mkati jinu, na chiheku chinu chikubhaje kamili.  
\v 12 Amuli jangu nde ajeji: Mpalanaye ngati nepani monumpali mwehapa.  
\v 13 Njeta mundu joabhi na upalu ukolongwa kupeta ghongone, mundu kuubhoha womi waki kwa ndandi ja bhakochi bhaki.  
\v 14 Mwehapa mbi bhakochi bhangu, ngati anantendiki ghanundaghalakile.  
\v 15 Nganundohi bhatumika kabhete, kwa ndandi mtumika ngacheamanya cheatenda bambo waki. Nambu mwehapa nundohiki bhakochi bhangu, maghambu numpwaghi mambu ghokapi ghanyowini kwa Atati wangu.  
\v 16 Nga mwehapa mwemunhawili nepani, nambu nepani nde nenunhawili mwehapa, nanatu numbekiki njenda mkapambikaje mapambiku, na mapambiku ghinu ghapataje kutamakila, nahuli lokapi lemundobha Atati kupetela lihina langu, ampekyaje.  
\v 17 Haghagha nundaghalaki mwehapa, nahuli mpalanaje.” 
\s1 Ndema ubhahakalila bhabhulwa 
\p  
\v 18 “Ngati bhandu bha pundema anabhunhakali mwehapa, mmanyi kubha bhakanhakali nepani mangane ja kunhakali mwehapa.  
\v 19 Ngati mkabhi bhandu bha pundema, ndema ukabya umpaliki bhabhabhi bhaki. Nambu kwa kubha mwehapa nga mabhandu bha pundema, nambu nepani nakunhawili kuhuma pundema, kwa ndandi jeniheji bhandu bha pundema bhunhakalila.  
\v 20 Nkombukaje malobhi ghangu ghanakumpwaghile, ‘Mtumika nga nkolongwa kupeta bambo waki. Ngati bhakang'ahiki nepani, anabhung'aha na mwehapa bhelabhela, na ngati bhakakamwi malobhi ghangu, anabhakamulaje na malobhi ghinu bhelabhela.’  
\v 21 Nambu ghanihagha ghokapi anabhuntendilaje mwehapa kwa ndandi ja lihina langu, maghambu ngachebhummanyi jombi joandumike.  
\v 22 Ngati nganakahikiki na kupwagha nabhu, ngabhakabhi na mahoku, nambu sajenu ngachebhabhili na cha kukopunganela kwa mahoku ghabhu.  
\v 23 Jola joanhakali nepani, anhakalila na Atati wangu bhelabhela.  
\v 24 Ngati nganakatendiki kwabhu mahengu ghangakughatenda mundu jongi jokapi, ngabhakabhi na mahoku. Nambu sajenu bhaweni ngangachu yenu na bhakali kutuhakalila nepani papamu na Atati wangu.  
\v 25 Nambu bhatendiki bhenibhela nahuli malobhi ghala ghaghalembakiki mu Shelia jabhu ghapitalyaje, ghaghapwagha, ‘Bhakanhakali waka.’ ” 
\p  
\v 26 “Nambu paanahikaje Mjangatila hoju, joananuntumaje kwinu kuhuma kwa Atati, yani, Roho Mhuhu wa chakaka joahuma kwa Atati, najombi anaanandilaje nepane.  
\v 27 Mwehapa nanamu mnandila, kwa ndandi mkabhi papamu na nepani kutumbu pakutumbula.” 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 “Numpwaghi mambu ghanihagha ghokapi, nahuli ngamwauleka uhobhalelu winu.  
\v 2 Bhandu anabhuntopula mwenga mu nyumba ya kuhimangani Bhayahude, na chikahi chihika kila mundu joanaankomaje akahambukya kubha antende Chapanga ibada.  
\v 3 Anabhuntendila mambu ghanihagha, kwa ndandi ngachebhummanyi Atati, wala nepani.  
\v 4 Nambu numpwaghili mambu ghanihagha, nahuli chikahi chela pachihikaje, mpata kukomboka kubha nyomwi kumpwaghila. 
\s1 Lihengu laka Roho Mhuhu 
\p “Ngachenumpwaghili mambu ghanihagha kutumbu pakutumbula, maghambu nakabhi papamu na mwehapa.”  
\v 5 Nambu sajenu nyenda kwaka jombi joandumike, na wala ngajoanalukila, “Bho, ujenda kwako?”  
\v 6 Nambu kwa ndandi numpwaghi mambu ghanihagha, mitima jinu jitwelili huzuni.  
\v 7 Nambu nepani numpwaghi chakaka, impalika mwehapa nepani mokaje, maghambu nangakubhoka nepani, Mjangatila hoju ngaahiki kwinu. Nambu nepani anambiti, ananuntuma kwinu.  
\v 8 Jombi paanahikaje, jonihoju anaabhalangiha bhandu bha pundema kubha maholalelu ghabhu nga manyahi panani ja mahoku, panani ja kujetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga, na panani ja utemulu waka Chapanga.  
\v 9 Kwa malobhi gha mahoku, maghambu ngachebhanhobhali nepani.  
\v 10 Kwa malobhi gha kujetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga, maghambu nyenda kwa Atati, na mwehapa ngamwimoni kabhete.  
\v 11 Kwa malobhi gha utemulu waka Chapanga, maghambu Shetani, nkolongwa wa ndema ghoni ajomwi kutemuliwa. 
\p  
\v 12 “Mi naghu mambu ghamaheli gha kumpwaghila, nambu kwa sajenu ngamuwezi kughakamula.  
\v 13 Nambu jombi paanahikaje, Roho Mhuhu wa chakaka, anaandonguha mwehapa mu chakaka jokapi. Maghambu ngayipwaghi kwa ndandi jaki mweni, nambu ghokapi ghayijowanaje kuhuma kwaka Chapanga anaaghapwaghaje, na mambu ghaghahika anaampwaghila malobhi ghaki.  
\v 14 Jombi anaanumbalyaje nepani, kwa ndandi anaatola ghaghabhi ghangu, na kumpwaghi mwehapa.  
\v 15 Ghokapi ghaabhi naghu Atati nde ghangu, nde ndandi nakapwaghiki Roho Mhuhu anaatola ghaghabhi ghangu, na kumpwaghi mwehapa.” 
\s1 Huzuni na chiheku 
\p  
\v 16 “Chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa ngamwimone, na kabhete, chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa anammonaje, maghambu nyenda kwa Atati.” 
\p  
\v 17 Panihapa bhakumu bha bhabhulwa bhaki bhakalaluhini, “Bho, lilobhi bhole leapwagha heli, paatupwaghi, ‘Chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa ngamwimone, na kabhete, chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa anammonaje?’ Na paapwagha, ‘Maghambu nyenda kwa Atati?’ ”  
\v 18 Bhela bhakapwaghike, “Bho, lilobhi bhole leniheli leapwagha, ‘Chihighali chikahi kichokopi?’ Ngachetumanyi alongale panani ja kike!” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu akamanyi kubha bhapala kundalukila, bhela akabhapwaghile, “Bho, mlaluhana panani ja ghala ghanapwaghiki, ‘Chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa ngamwimone, na kabhete, chihighali chikahi kichokopi, mwehapa anammonaje?’  
\v 20 Chakaka numpwaghila, mwehapa anamlelaje na kuombuleza, nambu bhandu bha pundema anabhahekalyaje. Na mwehapa anajumbina mitima jinu, nambu mabhinilu ghinu anaghang'anambuka na kubha chiheku.  
\v 21 Mbomba paalibhopola, lumbina lipyanda kwa ndandi chikahi chaki chihikike. Nambu anaajomwi kulibhopo mwana, ngacheakomboka kabhete mabhinilu ghala, kwa ndandi ja chiheku cha kubhelakeka mwana pundema.  
\v 22 Sajenu mwehapa mbi na mabhinilu, nambu nepani ananumbona kabhete, na mitima jinu anajihekalyaje, na chiheku chinu njeta mundu wa kumbokeha. 
\p  
\v 23 “Mu lichobha lela ngamwilalukile lilobhi lokapi. Numpwaghi Chakaka, ngati anamundobhiki Atati chindu chokapi kwa lihina langu, jombi anaampekyaje.  
\v 24 Mbaka sajenu ngachendobhiki chindu chokapi kwa lihina langu. Ndobhaje, na mwehapa anampataje, nahuli chiheku chinu chikamilikaje. 
\s1 Yesu auweziki ndema 
\p  
\v 25 “Numpwaghi mambu ghanihagha kwa ulenganesu. Nambu chikahi chihika ambapu nganipwaghi na mwehapa kabhete kwa ulenganesu, nambu ananumpwaghilaje hotuhotu malobhi gha Atati.  
\v 26 Mu lichobha lela mwilobhaje kwa lihina langu, na wala ngachenumpwaghila kubha nepani ananundobhila kwa Atati,  
\v 27 kwa ndandi Atati mwene ampala mwehapa. Maghambu mwehapa mumbaliki nepani, na kuhobhalela kubha nepani nakahumiki kwaka Chapanga.”  
\v 28 Nepani nakahumiki kwa Atati, nanatu nhikiki pani pundema, na kabhete nuleka ndema, na kujenda kwa Atati. 
\p  
\v 29 Bhela bhabhulwa bhaki bhakapwaghike, “Lingalyaje, sajenu upwagha hotuhotu, wala ngacheupwagha kwa malenganesu ghokapi ghala.  
\v 30 Sajenu tumanyi kubha wehapa umanyi mambu ghokapi, na wala ngachekubhi na ndandi jaka mundu kukulalukila, bhela tuhobhalela kubha ukahumiki kwaka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 31 Yesu akabhayangike, “Bho, sajenu le muhobhalela?  
\v 32 Lingalyaje, chikahi chihika, ena, chijomwi kuhika, pamwipechanganaje kila mundu kwaki, na kuneka nepani kanjika jangu. Nambu nepani ngachemi kanjika jangu, kwa ndandi Atati abhi papamu na nepani.  
\v 33 Numpwaghili mambu ghanihagha nahuli mpata kubha na lukwale mkati jangu. Pundema anampata ulale, nambu mulipekya mtima, kwa ndandi nepani niuweziki ndema!” 
\c 17  
\s1 Yesu abhalobhela bhabhulwa bhaki 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu paakajomwi kulongela malobhi ghanihagha, akalingali kunani kumahunde, na kupwagha, “Atati, lisaa lihikike. Undumbalyaje Mwana waku, nahuli najombi Mwana waku akulumbalyaje wehapa.  
\v 2 Ngati moumpeki lujiniku panani ja bhandu bhokapi, nahuli kwa bhokapi bhaumpekihe abhapekya womi wa mileli.  
\v 3 Na womi wa mileli nde ghongone, bhandu bhakumanya wehapa wa Chapanga wa kanjika wa chakaka, na Yesu Kristo joukantumike.  
\v 4 Nepani nukulumbalili pundema, nakabya nyomwile lihengu lela leukambekihe nilihengaje.  
\v 5 Sajenu Atati! Unumbalyaje nepani papamu na wehapa, kwa ulumbalilu ghola ghonakabhi naghu papamu na wehapa mangane ja kubhombakeka kwa ndema.” 
\p  
\v 6 “Nukutendiki umanyikanaje kwa bhandu bhala bhawambekihe pundema. Bhakabhi bhaku, ukambekihi nepani, na Lilobhi laku bhalijowine.  
\v 7 Sajenu bhamanyi kubha yokapi yewambekihe ihumiki kwaku.  
\v 8 Magambu malobhi ghala ghawambekihe nabhapekihi bhombi, na bhombi bhakaghajopalile. Na bhakamanyi chakaka kubha nakahumiki kwaku, na bhakahobhalili kubha wehapa nde wewandumike.” 
\p  
\v 9 Nepani nabhalobhela bhombi. Nepani ngachenulobhela ndema, nambu bhala bhaumbekihe, maghambu bhanihabha nde bhaku.  
\v 10 Bhokapi bhabhabhi bhangu nde bhaku, na bhabhabhi bhaku nde bhangu, nanatu numbaliwi mkati jabhu.  
\v 11 Nepani sajenu ngangubhi kabheti pundema, nambu bhombi bhakali bhabhi pundema, nanatu nhika kwaku. Atati Mhuhu, kwa makili gha lihina laku lewambekihe ubhalenda bhombi, nahuli bhabya chindu chimu ngati tepani motubhelile.  
\v 12 Panakabhi papamu nabhu pundema, nakabhalendiki kwa makili gha lihina laku lewambekihe, wala njeta jumu wabhu joakahobhike, nambu jola mwana wa kuhobha, nahuli Malembu Mahuhu ghatimilaje.  
\v 13 Na sajenu nhika kwaku, na malobhi ghangani naghalongela pundema, nahuli bhabya na chiheku changu chakabya chikamilike mkati jabhu.  
\v 14 Nepani nabhapeki lilobhi laku, na bhandu bha pundema bhatenda kubhahakalila, maghambu bhombi nga bha pundema ghoni, ngati nepani momeli nga wa pundema ghoni.  
\v 15 Nepani ngachenobha kubha ubhabhoha pundema, nambu ubhalenda na Mhakau jola.  
\v 16 Bhombi nga bha pundema ghoni, ngati nepani momeli nga wa pundema ghoni.  
\v 17 Ubhagholulaje kwa chakaka jela, lilobhi laku nde chakaka.  
\v 18 Ngati bhela mowandumi nepani pundema, nanatu bhelabhela nakabhatumiki bhombi pundema.  
\v 19 Na kwa ndandi jabhu niligholola namwete, nahuli nabhombi bhagholulikaje mu chakaka jela. 
\p  
\v 20 Wala nga bhanihabha pela bhanabhalobhela, nambu na bhala bhabhinhobhalyaje kwa ndandi ja lilobhi labhu.  
\v 21 Nobha nahuli bhokapi bhabya chindu chimu, ngati wehapa, Atati, moubheli mkati jangu, nanatu mkati jaku, bhanganya habha nabhombi bhabya mkati jitu. Nahuli bhandu bha pundema bhapata kuhobhalela kubha wehapa nde wewandumike.  
\v 22 Na ulumbalilu ghola ghowambeki nepani nabhapeki bhombi, nahuli bhabya chindu chimu ngati tepani motubheli chindu chimu.  
\v 23 Nepani mkati jabhu, na wehapa mkati jangu. Nahuli bhabya bhakamiliki mu chindu chimu. Nahuli bhandu bha pundema bhamanya kubha wehapa nde wewandumike, ubhapala bhombi ngati mowambali nepani. 
\p  
\v 24 “Atati, bhanihabha bhaumbekihe mbala bhabya papamu na nepani pokapi pamile, bhapata kuulinga ulumbalilu wangu ghoumbekihe. Maghambu ukambaliki mangani ja kutumbula kubhombakeka ndema.  
\v 25 Atati Wambone! Bhandu bha pundema ngachebhukumanye, nambu nepani nakakumanyi, nabhombi bhamanyiki kubha wehapa nde wewandumike.  
\v 26 Nanatu nilitendiki lihina laku limanyikanaje kwabhu, kabheti ananyendalyaje kulitenda limanyikanaje, nahuli upalu ghola ghowambaliki nepani ubya mkati jabhu, na nepani mya mkati jabhu.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Yesu akamulika 
\r Matayo 26:47-56; Mako 14:43-50; Luka 22:47-53 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu paakajomwi kundobha Chapanga, akabhokiki na bhabhulwa bhaki na kujenda kwihi ja kikoka Keduloni, pakukabhi na chijongu, akajingi jombi papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki.  
\v 2 Bhela Yuda, jola joapalikaje kung'anambuka Yesu, akapamanyi pandu pala. Maghambu Yesu akabhi ajenda konihoku pamaheli papamu na bhabhulwa bhaki.  
\v 3 Bhela Yuda, akabya atoliki lipogha la manjolinjoli bha Kiloma na bhalonda bha Nyumba jaka Chapanga bhabhakahumiki kwa ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku na Mafalisayo, bhakapiti konihoku bhakabya bhatotwi taa, na myengi, na mikoha na ndonga.  
\v 4 Yesu akabya amanyi ghala ghaghumpataje, akapiti palongi jabhu na kubhalalukila, “Bho, mundonda nane?”  
\v 5 Bhombi bhakamuyangike, “Yesu wa ku Nazaleti.” 
\p Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nde nepani.” 
\p Najombi Yuda, jola joakang'anambwiki Yesu, akabhi ajemiki papamu nabhu.  
\v 6 Yesu paakabhapwaghi, “Nde nepani,” bhakakelawiki chihanganyuma, na kuhabhuka pahi. 
\p  
\v 7 Bhela Yesu akabhalaluki kabhete, “Bho, mundonda nane?” 
\p Bhakamuyangike, “Yesu wa ku Nazaleti.” 
\p  
\v 8 Yesu akabhayangike, “Nyomwi kumpwaghila kubha nde nepani. Bhela ngati mnonda nepani, mwabhaleka bhanganya abhabha bhajendaje.”  
\v 9 Nahuli litimiaje lilobhi lela leakapwaghiki, “Atati, bhala bhawambekihe ngachenunhoiki hata jumu wabhu.” 
\p  
\v 10 Bhela Simoni Petulu akabhi na lipanga, akalihungwili na kunheketa likutu la kumalelelu laka mtumika waka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa. Mtumika hoju lihina laki alowakika Maliko.  
\v 11 Bhela Yesu akumpwaghi Petulu, “Ukelabhuwa lipanga laku mu ala jaki. Bho, chikombi cha mang'ahiku cheambeki Atati le nganinywelela?” 
\s1 Yesu palongi jaka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa 
\p  
\v 12 Bhela manjolinjoli bha Kiloma bhala na nkolongwa wabhu wa manjolinjoli papamu na ihongozi bha Bhayahude bhakunkamwili Yesu, na kunkonga.  
\v 13 Kutumbula bhakumpeliki kwaka Anasi. Nkohanu waka Kayafa, joakabhi Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa chaka chela.  
\v 14 Kayafa nde jola joakabhapeki bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude lilobhi lela la kubha impalika mundu jumu kupotela kwa ndandi ja bhandu bhokapi. 
\s1 Petulu ankana Yesu 
\r Matayo 26:69-70; Mako 14:66-68; Luka 22:55-57 
\p  
\v 15 Simoni Petulu papamu na mbulwa njaki bhakabhi bhunjengalela Yesu. Mbulwa jongi hoju akabhi amanyikana kwaka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa, akajingili papamu na Yesu mu liwangala laka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa.  
\v 16 Nambu Petulu akajemiki kunja ja ndyangu. Bhela mbulwa jongi joakamanyakini kwaka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa jola, akapitiki kunja, na kulongela na mwali joalendika pundyangu jola, na kundeta Petulu mkati.  
\v 17 Bhela mwali joakabhi alenda ndyangu jola akundaluki Petulu, “Bho, wehapa le nga jumu wa bhabhulwa bhaka mundu ajojo?” 
\p Petulu akayangike, “Nga nepane.” 
\p  
\v 18 Bhatumika bhala papamu na manjolinjoli bhakabhi bhajemiki, bhakanyatukya moto wa makalakala, maghambu kukabhi na imbepu. Petulu najombi akabhi ajemi papamu nabhu, akanyatukya moto. 
\s1 Mpenganyambiku nkolongwa andaluki Yesu 
\r Matayo 26:59-66; Mako 14:55-64; Luka 22:66-71 
\p  
\v 19 Bhela Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa akundaluki Yesu panani ja bhabhulwa bhaki, na panani ja mabholu ghaki.  
\v 20 Yesu akayangike, “Nepani nongili hotuhotu pundema wokapi. Machobha ghokapi molika mu nyumba ya kuhimanganila Bhayahude, na paliwangala la Nyumba jaka Chapanga, pabhalibhongana Bhayahude bhokapi. Na ngachenalongi lilobhi lokapi lela kwa kulihiya.  
\v 21 Bho, maghambu ki unalukila nepani? Ubhalalukya bhala bhabhajowini ghala ghanabhapwaghile. Kwa ndandi bhombi bhamanyi ghanakapwaghike.” 
\p  
\v 22 Bhela paakapwaghiki ghanihagha, jumu wa manjolinjoli joakabhi ajemiki pambipi naku, akundapwi Yesu lighanja la kumihu, na kupwagha, “Bho, bhenibhela nde moumuyangi Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu akamuyangike, “Anangati nongili lijambu lihakau, ulandilaje uhakau ghonongile palongi ja bhandu. Nambu anangati nongili chakaka, bho, maghambu kiki unapula?” 
\p  
\v 24 Bhela Anasi akumpeliki Yesu kwaka Kayafa Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa, koni akabya akongakiki. 
\s1 Petulu ankana Yesu kabhete 
\r Matayo 26:71-75; Mako 14:69-72; Luka 22:58-62 
\p  
\v 25 Chikahi hechi Simoni Petulu akabhi akali ajemiki akanyatukya moto. Bhakumu bha bhabhakabhi panipala bhakundaluki Petulu, “Bho, wehapa le nga wa jumu wa bhabhulwa bhake?” 
\p Petulu akakaniki, akapwaghaje, “Nga nepani.” 
\p  
\v 26 Jumu wa bhatumika bhaka Mpenganyambiku Nkolongwa, ndongu waka mundu jola Petulu joakunchekwi likutu, akundalukile, “Bho, nepani le ngachenukuweni kuchijongu kola ukabya papamu na Yesu?” 
\p  
\v 27 Bhela Petulu akakaniki kabhete, na palapala likongobhi lakabhekike. 
\s1 Yesu palongi jaka Pilato 
\r Matayo 27:1-2,11-14; Mako 15:1-5; Luka 23:1-5 
\p  
\v 28 Bhela bhakuntoliki Yesu kuhuma kwaka Kayafa na kumpeleka panyumba jaka mtawala wa Kiloma. Kukabhi lukela, nambu bheni ngachebhajingili mkati ja nyumba jaka Gavana, ngabhihika kubha bhahakau, nahuli bhapata kula Pasaka.  
\v 29 Bhela Pilato akapitiki kunja ja nyumba jaki, na kubhalalukila, “Bho, ndetiki matakilu bhole panani jaka mundu ajojo?” 
\p  
\v 30 Bhakamuyangike, “Ngati kukabhi mundu ajojo ngacheahengiki mahakau, ngatukundetiki kwaku.” 
\p  
\v 31 Pilato akabhapwaghile, “Haya muntola mwehapa mukuntemulaje kwa kulengana na shelia hinu.” 
\p Bhayahude bhakumpwaghile, “Tepani ngachetubhi na lujiniku lwa kuntemula mundu kupotela.”  
\v 32 Bhakalongi bhenibhela nahuli malobhi ghaakalongi Yesu, panani ja ntundu wa nyiwa jeayikuwaje ghapata kutimia. 
\p  
\v 33 Bhela Pilato akajingi kabhete munyumba jaki, akundohiki Yesu, na kundalukila, “Bho, wehapa le nde Unkolongwa wa Bhayahude?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu akamuyangike, “Bho, unalukila lilalukilu lendenu kubhokana na maholalelu ghaku au bhakakupwaghi bhandu bhangi malobhi panani jangu?” 
\p  
\v 35 Pilato akamuyangike, “Bho, nepani le nu Myahude?” Bhandu bhaku na ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku nde bhabhukuletiki kwangu. Bho, uhengiki kike? 
\p  
\v 36 Yesu akamuyangike, “Ukolongwa wangu nga wa ndema ghoni. Ngati ukolongwa wangu ukabhi wa ndema ghoni, bhatumika bhangu bhakabya bhangomanile, nahuli nganikamulika na bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude. Nambu ukolongwa wangu nga wa pani pundema!” 
\p  
\v 37 Bhela Pilato akumpwaghile, “Bho, henu wehapa le unkolongwa?” 
\p Yesu akamuyangike, “Wehapa upwaghike kubha nepani nunkolongwa. Nepani melakiki kwa ndandi ja ghangane, na kwa ndandi ja ghangane nakahiki pundema, nahuli nandila chakaka. Mundu jokapi joabhi wa chakaka anyowanela sauti jango.” 
\p  
\v 38 Pilato akalalukile, “Bho, chakaka nde kike?” 
\s1 Yesu atemulika kupotela 
\r Matayo 27:15-31; Mako 15:6-20; Luka 23:13-25 
\p Pilato paakalongi malobhi ghanihagha, akapitiki kabheti kunja na kubhapwaghila bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude bhabhakuntakili Yesu, “Nepani ngachemona lihoku lokapi lela kwaka mundu ajojo.  
\v 39 Nambu mabhanganya mbi na ntetu winu kubha chikahi cha Pasaka numbopulya mkongeka jumu jomumpala. Bho, mpala le numbopulya Nkolongwa wa Bhayahude ajojo?” 
\p  
\v 40 Bhombi bhakajamali kabhete, bhakapwaghaje, “Nga mundu hoju, nambu utubhopulya Balaba!” Bhela Balaba akabhi mnyaghula wa hindu ya bhandu. 
\c 19  
\p  
\v 1 Bhela Pilato akalaghalakili bhuntola Yesu, na kundapu iboku.  
\v 2 Nabhombi manjolinjoli bhakalokiki litaji la miha, na kunhwatika Yesu kumutu, na bhakunhwatiki ingobhu ja zambalau.  
\v 3 Bhakabhi bhunjendela na kumpwaghila, “Monile! Nkolongwa wa Bhayahude!” Na bhakundapwi maghanja kumihu. 
\p  
\v 4 Bhela Pilato akapitiki kabheti kunja, na kubhapwaghila, “Ndingalyaje! Nundeta Yesu kwinu, mpata kumanya kubha nepani ngachemweni lihakau lokapi lela la kuntemula kwaki.”  
\v 5 Panihapa Yesu akapitiki kunja, akabya awatiki litaji la miha lela, na ingobhu ja zambalau jela. Pilato akabhapwaghile, “Ndingalyaje! Mundu wene jopambane!” 
\p  
\v 6 Bhapenganyambiku bhakolongwa na bhalonda bha Nyumba jaka Chapanga pabhakumbweni, bhakajamalili, bhakapwaghaje, “Unhwamba punsalaba! Unhwamba punsalaba!” 
\p Pilato akabhapwaghile, “Muntola mabhete, mukunhwambaje. Maghambu nepani ngachemona lihakau la kuntemula kwaki.” 
\p  
\v 7 Bhayahude bhakamuyangike, “Tepani tubhi na shelia, na kubhokana na shelia heji, impalika kupotela, maghambu akalitendiki kubha Mwana waka Chapanga.” 
\p  
\v 8 Pilato paakajowini malobhi ghanihagha, akajowipi nakanopi.  
\v 9 Akajingi kabhete munyumba jaki ja kikolongwa jela na kundaluki Yesu, “Bho, wehapa uhumiki kwako?” 
\p Nambu Yesu ngacheakayangiki lilobhi lokapi lela.  
\v 10 Pilato akumpwaghile, “Bho, ngacheulonge na nepane? Bho, ngacheumanyi kubha nepani mi na lujiniku lwa kukubhopola au lujiniku lwa kukuwamba?” 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu akamuyangike, “Wehapa ngaukabhi na lujiniku lwokapi lola panani jangu, ngati ngaukajopali kuhuma kwaka Chapanga. Kwa ndandi jeniheji, jola joanetiki kwaku abhi na lihoku likolongwa nakanopi.” 
\p  
\v 12 Kutumbula panihapa Pilato akalondiki indela ja kumbopola Yesu. Nambu Bhayahude bhakajamalili, bhakapwaghaje, “Anaumbopuli mundu ajoju, wehapa nga unkochi waka Kaisali. Maghambu kila mundu joalitenda kubha nkolongwa ampenga Kaisali!” 
\p  
\v 13 Bhela, Pilato paakajowini malobhi ghanihagha, akundetiki Yesu kunja, akatami pachitehu chaki cha utemulu, pandu papalowakeka, “Lubhanja lwa Liganga,” au kwa Kiebulania, “Gabata.”  
\v 14 Na ghakabhi maandalilu gha Pasaka, ngati saa sita ja muhi. Pilato akabhapwaghi Bhayahude, “Ndingalyaje, nkolongwa winu!” 
\p  
\v 15 Nambu bhombi bhakajamalili, bhakapwaghaje, “Unkomaje! Unkomaje! Unhwamba punsalaba!” 
\p Pilato akabhapwaghile, “Bho, nunhwamba nkolongwa wino?” 
\p Ihongozi bha bhapenganyambiku bhakamuyangiki, “Tepani ngachetubhi na nkolongwa nambu Kaisali!” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhela Pilato akabhapeki Yesu kwabhu nahuli bhunhwambaje. 
\s1 Yesu awambakika punsalaba 
\r Matayo 27:32-44; Mako 15:21-32; Luka 23:26-43 
\p Nabhombi bhakuntoliki Yesu.  
\v 17 Yesu akabya autotwili msalaba waki, akapitiki na kujenda pandu papalowakeka, “Lifuvu la Mmutu,” au kwa Kiebulania, “Goligota.”  
\v 18 Bhakamuwambiki konihoku, na bhangi bhabheli papamu naku, jumu upambala wa kumalelelu, na jongi upambala wa kumangeja, na Yesu akabya pachilanda jabhu.  
\v 19 Pilato akalembiki anuwane, na kujibheka panani ja msalaba waka Yesu. Na jakalembakiki, “Yesu wa ku Nazaleti, Nkolongwa wa Bhayahude.”  
\v 20 Bhela anuwani jeniheji bhakajisomiki Bhayahude bhamaheli. Maghambu pandu pala paakawambakiki Yesu pakabhi pambipi na muchi. Na jakalembakiki kwa Kiebulania, na Kilumi, na Kigiliki.  
\v 21 Nambu bhapenganyambiku bhakolongwa na Bhayahude bhakumpwaghi Pilato, “Ngawilemba, ‘Nkolongwa wa Bhayahude,’ nambu ulemba, ‘Mundu ajoju akapwaghiki kubha, Nepani nde Nkolongwa wa Bhayahude.’ ” 
\p  
\v 22 Pilato akayangike, “Chenyomwi kulemba, nembike.” 
\p  
\v 23 Bhela manjolinjoli pabhakajomwi kunhwamba Yesu, bhakaitoliki ingobhu yaki, na kuighabha mapogha ncheche, kwa kila linjolinjoli lipogha laki. Nambu bhakajetangani likanzu laki lela ngabhalikachula, maghambu lakabhi nga mshonu, nambu lilokakiki kutumbu kunani mbaka pahi.  
\v 24 Bhela bhakapwaghani bheni kwa bheni, “Ngatujikachula, nambu tujilapulya kula, jibya jaka nane.” Nahuli ghatimiaje Malembu Mahuhu ghaghapwagha, 
\q1 “Bhakaghabhini ingobhu yangu, 
\q1 na kanzu jangu bhakajilapuli kula.” 
\m Bhenibhela nde mobhakahengi manjolinjoli bhala. 
\p  
\v 25 Na pambipi na msalaba waka Yesu akabhi ajemiki mabhu waka Yesu, na ndombu wa mabhu waki, na Malia nhwanu waka Kileopa, na Malia Magidalena.  
\v 26 Bhela Yesu paakumbweni mabhu waki, na mbulwa joakumpaliki jola ajemiki pambipi, akumpwaghi mabhu waki, “Amabhu, hajoju nde mwana waku.” 
\p  
\v 27 Kebhete akumpwaghi mbulwa jola, “Lingalyaje, hajoju nde mabhu waku.” Na kutumbu chikahi chela mbulwa jola akuntoliki mabhu waka Yesu kunyumba jaki. 
\s1 Yesu apotela 
\r Matayo 27:45-56; Mako 15:33-41; Luka 23:44-49 
\p  
\v 28 Paghajomwiki ghanihagha, Yesu akamanyi kubha ghokapi ghajomwike. Nahuli ghapitalyaje Malembu Mahuhu, akapwaghike, “Mona inywita.” 
\p  
\v 29 Panihapa pakabhi na mbale jejitweli siki. Bhela bhakatobhali siponji mu siki jela, na kujibheka mu ufito wa nkongu wa hisopo, na kumpelakela mundomu.  
\v 30 Yesu paakayomwi kujionja siki heji, akapwaghike, “Ghajomwike!” 
\p Akajinamishi mmutu waki, na kuheketa roho. 
\s1 Yesu ahomangeka nkoha 
\p  
\v 31 Bhela bhakolongwa bha Bhayahude kwa kubha lakabhi nde lichobha la Ijumaa, yani, lichobha la Maandalio mangani ja Lichobha la Sabato na hyegha ngaitama punsalaba Lichobha la Sabato, maghambu Lichobha la Sabato lakabhi lichobha likolongwa, bhakundobhiki Pilato bhahekata magholu gha bhala bhabhawambakike, na bhakabhohakikaje.  
\v 32 Bhela manjolinjoli bhakapiti, bhakunhekiti magholu wa kutumbula, na wa kabheli, joakawambakiki punsalaba papamu na Yesu.  
\v 33 Nambu pabhakunhiki Yesu, na kumbona ajomwi kupotela, ngachebhunhekiti magholu.  
\v 34 Nambu linjolinjoli jumu akunhomiki mwindeta jaka Yesu kwa nkoha, na palapala ukapitiki mwahi na machi.  
\v 35 Mundu joakaweni mambu ghanihagha nde joabhohika ulandilu, na ulandilu waki nde wa chakaka. Najombi amanyi kubha alongela chakaka, nahuli nanamu mpata kuhobhalela.  
\v 36 Mambu ghanihagha ghakahengakiki nahuli Malembu Mahuhu ghapata kupitalila, “Njeta hata chihupa chaki chimu chechihekatwaje.”  
\v 37 Na kabheti Malembu ghangi ghapwagha, “Anabhundinga jola jobhunhotwile.” 
\s1 Yesu abhekakeka mulitengele 
\r Matayo 27:57-61; Mako 15:42-47; Luka 23:50-56 
\p  
\v 38 Paghapetiki mambu ghanihagha, Yusufu mundu wa ku Alimataya, akunjopiki Pilato anjetakalya kujiheleha hyegha jaka Yesu punsalaba. Yusufu akabhi nde mbulwa waka Yesu, nambu kwa kulihiya, kwa choghohi ja Bhayahude, na Pilato akunjetakalile. Bhela Yusufu akapiti, na kujitola hyegha jaka Yesu.  
\v 39 Yusufu akalongini na Nikodemu jola ambaju pakutumbula akunjendi Yesu ikilu, akaletiki mahangaghanu gha manungilu ghaghalowakeka manemane na ubani, ngati kilo selasini.  
\v 40 Bhokapi bhabeli bhakajitoliki hyegha jaka Yesu, bhakajikongiki sanda ja ingobhu jinyahi jihuhu papamu na manungilu ghala, ngati moubheli ntetu wa Bhayahude wa kutagha.  
\v 41 Na palapala paakawambakiki Yesu pala, pakabhi na chijongu, na mkati ja chijongu chela kukabhi na litengeli lahenu, lelu ngachealabhali kutaghakika mundu.  
\v 42 Bhela maghambu lakabhi lichobha la Bhayahude la Maandalio gha Lichobha la Sabato na litengeli lakabhi pambipi, bhakajibhekiki hyegha jaka Yesu mulitengele. 
\c 20  
\s1 Yesu ahyoka kuhuma kwa bhakuwa 
\r Matayo 28:1-8; Mako 16:1-8; Luka 24:1-12 
\p  
\v 1 Lukela pachibhombu lichobha la Jumapili, kukabya kukali na lwihi, Malia Magidalena akapiti kulitengeli, na akaliweni liganga lela libhohakiki pundyangu wa litengeli.  
\v 2 Bhela akakembili imbelu mbaka kwaka Simoni Petulu na mbulwa jongi jola ambaju Yesu akumpaliki, na kubhapwaghila, “Bhumbohiki Bambo mulitengeli, wala ngachetumanyi kobhumbekike.” 
\p  
\v 3 Bhela Petulu papamu na mbulwa jongi jola, bhakabhokiki na kujenda kulitengeli.  
\v 4 Bhakakembili imbelu bhokapi bhabheli, nambu mbulwa jongi jola akakembili nakanopi kumpeta Petulu, na kubha wa kutumbula kuhika kulitengeli.  
\v 5 Akajinimi na kulingalila mulitengeli mola, akaiweni itambala ya sanda mkati mola, nambu ngacheajingile.  
\v 6 Simoni Petulu najombi akajengalile, akajingili mkati ja litengeli, na akaiweni itambala ya sanda yela mkati ja litengele,  
\v 7 na chitambala chechakabhi bhahyongalwi pamutu jaka Yesu. Ngachechaghonili papamu na itambala ya sanda yela, nambu chakabhi chikunjakiki na kubhekakeka kutali pandu pa kanjika jaki.  
\v 8 Bhela mbulwa jongi joakalonguli kuhika palitengeli jola, najombi akajingili mkati, akaweni, na kuhobhalela.  
\v 9 Maghambu mbaka chikahi chenihechi bhakabhi bhakali ngakumanya Malembu Mahuhu ghala kubha, ikabhi impalika Yesu ayokaje kabhete kuhuma kwa bhakuwa.  
\v 10 Bhela bhabhulwa bhala bhakakelawiki kabhete kunyumba jabhu. 
\s1 Yesu ampitalila Malia Magidalena 
\r Matayo 28:9-10; Mako 16:9-11 
\p  
\v 11 Nambu Malia akabhi ajemiki pambipi na litengeli akalelaje. Chikahi paakabhi alela, akajinimi na kulingalila mkati ja litengeli.  
\v 12 Akabhaweni bhatumika bhabheli bha kunani kwaka Chapanga, bhawati ingobhu ihuhu kupukupu, bhatami pala pabhajighoniki hyegha jaka Yesu, jumu kumutu, na jongi kumagholu.  
\v 13 Bhombi bhakumpwaghi Malia, “Mbomba, bho, mbona ulela?” 
\p Malia akabhayangike, “Bhumbohiki Bambo wangu, wala nepani ngachemanyi kobhumbekike!” 
\p  
\v 14 Malia paakajomwi kulonge ghanihagha, akang'anambwiki kunyuma, na kumbona Yesu ajemiki, koni akabya ngakumanya kubha nde Yesu.  
\v 15 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Mbomba, bho, ulela kike?” Bho, undonda nane? 
\p Jombi koni akaholakya kubha nde mlonda wa chijongu, akumpwaghile, “Nkolongwa, anangati untoliki wehapa, umbwaghilaje paumbekike, nanatu ananuntolaje.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Malia.” 
\p Malia akang'anambwiki, na kumpwaghila kwa Kiebulania, “Laboni!” Yani, “Mbola!” 
\p  
\v 17 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ngawingamula, maghambu nakali ngachembiti kwa Atati wangu.” Nambu ujenda kwa bhalongu bhangu ukabhapwaghilaje, “Ng'oloka kujenda kwa Atati wangu, najombi nde Atati winu, na kwaka Chapanga wangu, najombi nde Chapanga winu.” 
\p  
\v 18 Malia Magidalena akapiti na kubhapwaghila bhabhulwa malobhi, “Numbweni Bambo!” Na kubha ampwaghi mambu ghanihagha. 
\s1 Yesu abhapitali bhabhulwa bhaki 
\r Matayo 28:16-20; Mako 16:14-18; Luka 24:36-49 
\p  
\v 19 Kukabhi pakamihi, lichobha lela la kutumbula la juma la Jumapile. Bhabhulwa bhaki bhakabhi bhalibhongini papamu, milyangu jakabya jijighaliki kwa ndandi ja kubhajoghopa ihongozi bha Bhayahude. Yesu akahikike, akajemiki pachilanda jabhu, na kubhapwaghila, “Lukwali lubya na mwenga!”  
\v 20 Na paakapwaghiki ghanihagha, akabhalangi mabhoku ghaki na indeta jaki. Bhela bhabhulwa bhala bhakahekalili namaa, pabhakumbweni Bambo.  
\v 21 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghi kabhete, “Lukwali lubya na mwenga, ngati Atati moandumi nepani, nepani nanatu nuntuma mwehapa.”  
\v 22 Paakajomwi kulonge ghanihagha, akabhapulali na kubhapwaghila, “Njopalyaje Roho Mhuhu.  
\v 23 Bhokapi bhamwabhokia mahoku, bhabhohakike, na bhokapi bhamwakongila mahoku, bhakongakike.” 
\s1 Yesu na Tomaso 
\p  
\v 24 Nambu Tomaso, jumu wa bhabhulwa komi na bhabheli bhala, joalowakika Mabhela, ngacheakabhi papamu nabhu chikahi pahikika Yesu.  
\v 25 Bhela bhabhulwa bhangi bhakumpwaghile, “Tumbweni Bambo.” 
\p Tomaso akabhapwaghile, “Nepani nangakughabhona makumba gha misumali mumabhoku ghaki, na kubheka lukonji lwangu pa likumba la misumali, na kubheka lukonji lwangu pa indeta jaki, nganhobhaleli hata pachokope.” 
\p  
\v 26 Paghapetiki machobha nane, bhabhulwa bhaki bhakabhi mkati kabhete, na Tomaso akabya papamu nabhu. Bhela Yesu akahikike, na milyangu jijighalike, akajemiki pachilanda jabhu, na kupwagha, “Lukwali lubya na mwenga.”  
\v 27 Bhela akumpwaghi Tomaso, “Uletaje pambani lukonji lwaku, na ughalinga mabhoku ghangu, uletaje na chiwoku chaku ukamulaje mu indeta jangu, wala ngawikubha na choghohi, nambu uhobhalyaje.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tomaso akayangiki, na kumpwaghila, “Bambo wangu na Chapanga wangu!” 
\p  
\v 29 Yesu akumpwaghi Tomaso, “Bho, wehapa le uhobhalili maghambu utehi kumona? Bhapengaliki bhala bhanga kumona, nambu bhahobhalela.” 
\s1 Ndandi ja chitabu chenu 
\p  
\v 30 Bhela kubhi kabhete na nginyulila yengi yamaheli yeakahengiki Yesu palongi ja bhabhulwa bhaki, yangakulembakeka mu chitabu chenu.  
\v 31 Nambu yenjenu ilembakiki nahuli mmanya kubha Yesu nde Kristo, Mwana waka Chapanga, na kwa kunhobhalela jombi mbya na womi wa chakaka kwa kupetela lihina laki. 
\c 21  
\s1 Yesu abhapitalila bhabhulwa saba 
\p  
\v 1 Paghapetiki mambu ghanihagha Yesu akalilangi kabhete kwa bhabhulwa bhaki, pamaheku ja Bahali ja Tibelia, najombi akabhonakini ana:  
\v 2 Simoni Petulu, na Tomaso joalowakeka Mabhela, na Nathanaeli wa ku Kana ja ku Galilaya, na bhana bhabheli bhaka Zebedayo, na bhabhulwa bhangi bhabheli, bhakabhi papamu.  
\v 3 Simoni Petulu akabhapwaghi bhajaki, “Nyenda kulobha homba.” 
\p Nabhombi bhakumpwaghile, “Natatu anatujenda papamu na wehapa.” Bhela bhakabhokiki, bhakakweliki mu liboti, nambu ikilu jela ngachebhapatiki chindu.  
\v 4 Lukela pakwachile, Yesu akajemiki mumaheku, nambu bhabhulwa ngachebhamanyi kubha akabhi nde Yesu.  
\v 5 Bhela Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Bhanango, bho, mbi na homba?” 
\p Bhakamuyangiki, “Njeta.” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Mpendakya nkwabhu upambala wa kumalelelu wa liboti linu, nanamu anampata homba.” Bhela bhakapendakili, wala sajenu ngachebhaweziki kuhuta kabhete kwa ndandi ja kujoloka kwa homba. 
\p  
\v 7 Bhela mbulwa joakapalakiki na Yesu jola akumpwaghi Petulu, “Nde Bambo!” Najombi Simoni Petulu paakajowini kubha nde Bambo, akalikongiki ingobhu jaki, maghambu akahuliki ingobhu ja kunja, na kulilekela mubahali.  
\v 8 Bhabhulwa bhangi bhala bhakahikiki na liboti heli, maghambu bhakabhi nga kutali na kumaheku, nambu bhakabhi ngati utali wa mita mia moja kuhuma kundema, koni bhakahuta nkwabhu wana homba.  
\v 9 Bhela pabhaheli kumaheku, bhakauweni moto wa makalakala, na panani jaki bhajochiki homba, na libumunda.  
\v 10 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Ndeta pambani homba yakumu yendobhiki sajeno.” 
\p  
\v 11 Simoni Petulu akakweliki mu liboti, akauhutiki nkwawu kumaheku, utweli homba ikoluikolu, mia moja hamsini na tatu. Hata koni homba ikabhi yamaheli ntundu ghonihoghu, nambu nkwabhu ngachewakachwike.  
\v 12 Yesu akabhapwaghile, “Nhwika nkula chilebhi cha lukela.” Wala nga mundu pachilanda ja bhabhulwa bhala joakalengiki kundalukila kubha wehapa wa nane, maghambu bhakamanyi kubha nde Bambo.  
\v 13 Yesu akahikiki, na kutola libumunda, na kubhapekeha, na homba akahengiki bhelabhela. 
\p  
\v 14 Haje jakabhi mala ja katatu kwaka Yesu kubhapitalila bhabhulwa bhaki, kutumbula paakahyokiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa. 
\s1 Yesu na Petulu 
\p  
\v 15 Bhela pabhakajomwi kula, Yesu akumpwaghi Simoni Petulu, “Simoni mwana waka Yohana! Bho, umbala nepani kuliku bhanganya abhabha?” 
\p Petulu akayangiki, “Ena, Bambo, wehapa umanyi kubha nukupala.” 
\p Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ulehaje mambelele ghangu!”  
\v 16 Akumpwaghi kabhete pakabheli, “Simoni mwana waka Yohana! Bho, umbala nepani?” 
\p Petulu akayangiki, “Ena, Bambo, wehapa umanyi kubha nukupala!” 
\p Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ulehaje mambelele ghangu!”  
\v 17 Yesu akundaluki kabhete pakatatu, “Simoni mwana waka Yohana! Bho, umbala nepani?” 
\p Petulu akayomike maghambu akundaluki pakatatu, “Bho, umbala nepani?” Bhela akumpwaghile, “Bambo, wehapa umanyi ghokapi, wehapa umanyi kubha nukupala.” 
\p Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ulehaje mambelele ghangu!”  
\v 18 Nukupwaghi chakaka, paukabhi unkombo, ukabhi ulikonga wamwete na kujenda koupala. Nambu pawibya ukongapile, wihatambula mabhoku ghaku, na jongi anaakukongaje na kukupeleka kwanga kupala wehapa kujenda.  
\v 19 Kwa kupwagha malobhi ghanihagha, Yesu akalangi kubha kwa ntundu bhole Petulu anakuwaje nahuli kundumbali Chapanga. Bhela paakalongi ghanihagha, Yesu akumpwaghi Petulu, “Unyengalyaje!” 
\s1 Yesu na mbulwa joakumpaliki 
\p  
\v 20 Petulu akang'anambwiki na kumbona mbulwa jola joakapalakiki na Yesu. Jonihoju nde mbulwa jola joakajeghamaki pachihimba chaka Yesu chikahi cha kula chilebhi cha pakamihi, na kulalukila, “Bambo, bho, nane joakung'anambukaje?”  
\v 21 Bhela Petulu paakumbweni jonihoju, akumpwaghi Yesu, “Bambo, na ajoju anaatenda kike?” 
\p  
\v 22 Yesu akumpwaghile, “Ngati anambaliki ajoju atama mbaka panihikaje, bho, wehapa upala kike? Wehapa unyengalya nepani.” 
\p  
\v 23 Bhela lilobhi leniheli lakajaghani pachilanda ja bhahobhalela kubha mbulwa jola ngaakuwe. Nambu Yesu ngacheakumpwaghi kubha ngaakuwe, nambu, “Ngati anambaliki ajoju atama mbaka panihikaje, bho, wehapa upala kike?” 
\p  
\v 24 Hajoju nde mbulwa jola joaghalandila mambu ghanihagha, na nde joaghalembiki mambu ghanihagha. Natatu tumanyi kubha ghaaghapwaghiki nde gha chakaka. 
\s1 Ujomukelu 
\p  
\v 25 Kubhi kabhete na mambu ghangi ghamaheli ghaakahengiki Yesu. Ghaghu anangati ghakalembakiki limu limu, nholake hata ndema wokapi ngaukajaghanile kwa itabu yela yeikalembakikaje. Amina.